0reflects%20the%20growing%20reality%20in%20the%20industry%20that%20smartphones%20aren't%20powerful%20enough%20to%20run%20the%20most%20advanced%20AI%20models%20entirely%20on-device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20I%20expected%2C%20Apple%20is%20going%20to%20punt%20the%20'on-device'%20story%20for%20Apple%20Intelligence%20and%20push%20towards%20the%20'private%20cloud%20compute'%20story%20for%20the%20models%20that%20you'll%20actually%20want%20to%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20Warren%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20glad%20on-device%20isn't%20going%20away%2C%20but%20it's%20clear%20a%20hybrid%20approach%20is%20absolutely%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20Warren%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20probably%20reach%20the%20point%20in%20the%20future%20where%20you%20could%20do%20good-enough%20on-device%20processing%20for%20certain%20tasks%2C%20but%20that%20day%20isn't%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e106bad3-fa76-4ce0-b4c6-3b6950b0ccd2%5C%22%3EBen%20Bajarin%2C%20CEO%20and%20principal%20analyst%20at%20Creative%20Strategies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBajarin%20said%20that%20Apple%20seems%20to%20be%20turning%20Siri%20into%20a%20central%20hub%20for%20a%20one-stop%20AI%20experience%20rather%20than%20a%20collection%20of%20separate%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20talk%20about%20enterprise%20workflow%20control%20plane%2C%20the%20Apple%20opportunity%20here%20is%20Siri%20is%20turning%20into%20the%20control%20plane%20for%20consumer%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Bajarin%20wrote%20on%20X%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPersonal%20context%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparent-screen-time-rules-kids-benefited-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escreen%20awareness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20app%20actions%2C%20writing%2C%20search%2C%20and%20visual%20intelligence%20route%20through%20one%20assistant%20layer%2C%20which%20is%20a%20different%20product%20experience%20all%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Bajarin%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bcc5eda-d306-424d-a287-44dd7c462986%5C%22%3EMax%20Weinbach%2C%20consumer%20technology%20analyst%20at%20Creative%20Strategies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWeinbach%20wrote%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20Siri%20upgrade%20is%20potentially%20bad%20news%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feveryone-is-building-everything-openai-anthropic-lovable-cursor-canva-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20looking%20to%20build%20consumer%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20new%20Siri%20and%20AI%20features%20are%20good%2C%20and%20Apple%20can%20provide%20them%20for%20free%20with%20every%20new%20Apple%20device%2C%20everyone%20should%20be%20terrified%20of%20what%20happens%20to%20the%20AI%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Weinbach%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSiri%20AI%20is%20basically%20what%20most%20consumers%20use%20ChatGPT%20and%20Gemini%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Weinbach%20added%20in%20a%20follow-up%20post.%20%26quot%3BRIP%20consumer%20ambitions%20for%20AI%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f67a6d4-1ded-414c-bbc4-f472f611f6b8%5C%22%3EAlex%20Heath%2C%20tech%20journalist%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222965%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22APRIL%2007%3A%20Alex%20Heath%20speaks%20onstage%20during%20the%20%26quot%3BBret%20Taylor's%20View%20from%20the%20Top%26quot%3B%20panel%20at%20the%20HumanX%20Conference%20San%20Franciso%202026%20at%20Moscone%20Center%20South%20on%20April%2007%2C%202026%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20California.%20(Photo%20by%20Big%20Event%20Media%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20HumanX%20Conference)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a275a7b5bcf40c28b6b0674%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221976%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlex%20Heath%20said%20in%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20X%20that%20Apple%20is%20aiming%20for%20the%20same%20thing%20as%20the%20big%20AI%20players.%3Cp%3EBig%20Event%20Media%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20HumanX%20Conference%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHeath%20said%20in%20a%20series%20of%20tweets%20that%20Apple%20is%20aiming%20for%20exactly%20what%20the%20big%20AI%20players%20are%3A%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20personalized%2C%20all-knowing%2Fpresent%20assistant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Apple%20is%20showing%20%E2%80%94%20Siri%20understanding%20whatever%20is%20on%20an%20iPhone's%20screen%20and%20providing%20contextual%20responses%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20huge%20unlock%20if%20it%20works%20as%20shown%2C%26quot%3B%20Heath%20wrote%20on%20X%20on%20Monday.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BAlso%20shows%20how%20Apple%20continues%20to%20leverage%20platform%20control%20to%20do%20things%20folks%20at%20the%20app%20layer%20can't%2C%26quot%3B%20Heath%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeath%20was%20previously%20a%20senior%20reporter%20for%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a3e282b-8c28-402b-9b49-7ebebe8c1e1e%5C%22%3EErnest%20Wong%2C%20head%20of%20research%20at%20Baskin%20Wealth%20Management%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20lengthy%20introduction%20of%20its%20new%20child%20safety%20feature%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20perfect%20example%26quot%3B%20of%20%26quot%3Bstrategy%20credit%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20an%20uncomplicated%20decision%20that%20improves%20the%20company's%20image%20relative%20to%20other%20competitors%2C%20Wong%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20easy%20decision%20for%20Apple%20that%20simultaneously%20brings%20kids%2Fteens%20into%20their%20ecosystem%20and%20handicaps%20competitors%20(social%20media%20apps)%2C%20and%20looks%20good%20while%20doing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Wong%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a4e7b3a-22ae-4482-b040-69a5134b92ab%5C%22%3EChris%20Pirillo%2C%20founder%20of%20LockerGnome%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224942%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22MAY%2004%3A%20Geek%20culture%20expert%20Chris%20Pirillo%20attends%20the%20%23RoarForChange%20celebration%20at%20Disney%20store%20on%20May%204%2C%202018%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20California.%20(Photo%20by