ttention.%20But%20parents%20don't%20just%20need%20more%20controls.%20We%20need%20the%20controls%20to%20actually%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Stern%20added%20in%20subsequent%20posts%20regarding%20Apple's%20child%20safety%20updates.%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20there's%20a%20major%20under-the-hood%20improvement%20here%20focused%20on%20syncing%2C%20reliability%20and%20consistency%20across%20devices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a36a5f6-c1b8-483c-88da-bed335ce7f01%5C%22%3EDan%20Ives%2C%20tech%20analyst%20at%20Wedbush%20Securities%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIves%20said%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Monday%20that%20Apple%20was%20finally%20delivering%20on%20what%20it%20promised%20two%20years%20ago%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Brobust%20AI%20strategy%20and%20the%20announcement%20of%20Siri%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20this%20was%20an%20impressive%20event%20that%20did%20not%20disappoint%20as%20Cook%20and%20Apple%20finally%20unveiled%20an%20AI%20strategy%20that%20will%20unleash%20the%20true%20monetization%20opportunity%20for%20AI%20in%20the%20Cupertino%20consumer%20ecosystem%20after%20a%20few%20years%20of%20promise%20%E2%80%A6%20now%20it's%20finally%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-smart-people-are-saying-about-apple-ai-announcements-wwdc-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780968937000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2748b65bcf40c28b6b0656%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-smart-people-are-saying-about-apple-ai-announcements-wwdc-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tech%20industry%20leaders%20are%20weighing%20in%20on%20Apple's%20AI%20updates%20across%20its%20ecosystem%2C%20including%20on%20Siri%2C%20call%20assistance%2C%20and%20photo%20editing%20tools.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li%2CLloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A100%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20moved%20from%20Kansas%20City%20to%20Thailand%20with%203%20kids.%20We%20spend%20less%20time%20rushing%20and%20more%20time%20together.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221803%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20family%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%2C%20Thailand.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d43042ab5f9757add75ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221352%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClea%20Barry%20moved%20from%20the%20US%20to%20Chiang%20Mai%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20their%20three%20kids.%3Cp%3EArada%20Photography.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EClea%20Barry%2C%2044%2C%20left%20the%20US%20for%20Thailand%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20their%20three%20kids%20in%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETo%20make%20the%20move%20work%2C%20her%20husband%20accepted%20a%20teaching%20job%20at%20an%20international%20school%20in%20Chiang%20Mai.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20says%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20have%20been%20able%20to%20enjoy%20their%20kids'%20childhood%20years%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Clea%20Barry%2C%2044%2C%20an%20interior%20designer%20who%20moved%20from%20Kansas%20City%20to%20Chiang%20Mai%2C%20Thailand%2C%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20three%20kids%20in%202022.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20met%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20our%20shared%20love%20of%20travel%20brought%20us%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20we%20lived%20in%20several%20cities%20across%20the%20US%20with%20our%20three%20kids%2C%20including%20San%20Diego%20and%20Denver.%20Before%20moving%20abroad%2C%20we%20were%20living%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-cost-of-living-nyc-kansas-city-midwest-rent-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKansas%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20my%20husband%20taught%20middle%20school%20and%20I%20worked%20as%20an%20interior%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20traveled%20quite%20a%20bit%20for%20work.%20Life%20with%20little%20kids%20already%20felt%20hectic%2C%20and%20then%20the%20pandemic%20happened.%20After%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20of%20online%20school%2C%20we%20felt%20ready%20for%20a%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22935%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20family%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%2C%20Thailand.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d46c12e5a80cfe0501b25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22701%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETo%20make%20the%20move%20happen%2C%20her%20husband.%20accepted%20a%20job%20to%20teach%20at%20an%20international%20school%20in%20Thailand.%3Cp%3EArada%20Photography.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20friends%20working%20abroad%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-china-live-abroad-guangzhou-teach-english-gen-zers-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einternational%20teachers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20seeing%20their%20experiences%20inspired%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20a%20good%20opportunity%20for%20my%20husband%20to%20teach%20abroad%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20while%20our%20kids%20attended%20the%20same%20school.%20It%20felt%20like%20a%20chance%20for%20all%20of%20us%20to%20experience%20life%20in%20a%20new%20country%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd954b10-1799-40b4-a355-a9d7f6054efb%5C%22%3EA%20new%20chapter%20abroad%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20had%20considered%20moving%20abroad%20before%2C%20and%20had%20even%20received%20a%20few%20offers%20over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20timing%20never%20felt%20quite%20right.%20However%2C%20when%20a%20teaching%20opportunity%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-early-chiang-mai-thailand-slow-life-financial-security-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChiang%20Mai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20city%20in%20northern%20Thailand%2C%20came%20up%20in%202022%2C%20we%20jumped%20at%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20you%20relocated%20abroad%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20to%20Asia%20%E2%80%94%20for%20career%20opportunities%2C%20retirement%2C%20or%20lower%20living%20costs%3F%20We%20want%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Fill%20out%20this%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdxVL1zX0AV0FiTKnYB72xTcK5G4gxa8o5PwKsxTEwmgZJg1A%2Fviewform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eshort%20form%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20to%20share%20your%20story.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20I%20had%20already%20scaled%20back%20my%20work%20after%20our%20third%20child%2C%20and%20I%20was%20freelancing%20remotely%2C%20which%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20us%20to%20move.%20It%20also%20helped%20that%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20had%20visited%20Chiang%20Mai%20on%20our%20honeymoon%20in%202009%2C%20so%20we%20knew%20we%20loved%20the%20Thai%20culture%2C%20food%2C%20and%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20room.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d422f2e5a80cfe0501b1c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20family%20lives%20in%20a%20three-bedroom%20house%20about%2015%20minutes%20outside%20of%20Chiang%20Mai%20city%20center.%3Cp%3EClea%20Barry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20talked%20to%20our%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20who%20were%209%2C%207%2C%20and%202%20at%20that%20point%20%E2%80%94%20about%20the%20move%2C%20we%20framed%20it%20as%20a%20family%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20showed%20them%20YouTube%20videos%20about%20fun%20things%20they%20could%20try%20in%20Thailand%2C%20such%20as%20rolled%20ice%20cream%2C%20a%20popular%20dessert%20available%20at%20the%20night%20markets.%20That%20really%20excited%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202022%2C%20we%20packed%20up%20our%20bags%20and%20officially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirees-left-america-moved-to-chiang-mai-slower-affordable-life-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Chiang%20Mai%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20plan%20was%20to%20live%20for%20two%20years%2C%20but%20now%20it's%20been%20four.%20We're%20living%20in%20a%20three-bedroom%20home%20in%20Hang%20Dong%2C%20a%20district%20about%2015%20minutes%20outside%20Chiang%20Mai's%20city%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20bedrooms%20in%20a%20family%20home%20in%20Chiang%20Mai.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d422eb4fb977f35982a87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERent%20is%20about%20%24980%20each%20month.%3Cp%3EClea%20Barry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20came%20furnished%2C%20including%20plants.%20We%20have%20a%20pool%20and%20a%20garden%2C%20and%20it's%20an%20eight-minute%20drive%20to%20the%20international%20school.%20There's%20a%20coffee%20shop%20across%20the%20street%2C%20and%20we're%20also%20right%20by%20walking%20trails.%20Rent%20is%2032%2C000%20Thai%20baht%2C%20or%20about%20%24975%2C%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20kids%20have%20adjusted%20well.%20Since%20people%20move%20in%20and%20out%20of%20Chiang%20Mai%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20it's%20common%20for%20a%20new%20student%20to%20arrive%20in%20August%2C%20January%2C%20or%20any%20other%20time.%20Instead%20of%20thinking%20it's%20strange%2C%20the%20kids%20get%20excited.%20They're%20very%20open%20to%20meeting%20new%20people%20because%20they%20know%20everyone%20comes%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20volunteering%20at%20my%20kids'%20school%20over%20the%20holiday%20season%2C%20and%20that%20experience%20has%20been%20great%20because%20I%20get%20to%20see%20my%20kids%20at%20school%2C%20have%20lunch%20with%20them%2C%20and%20head%20home%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20days%20when%20I'm%20not%20volunteering%20at%20school%2C%20I%20drop%20off%20my%20kids%20at%208%20o'clock%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20head%20home%20to%20do%20my%20design%20work%2C%20then%20pick%20them%20up%20again%20in%20the%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20pool%20and%20outdoor%20area.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d422eb4fb977f35982a88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221050%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShe%20says%20the%20lifestyle%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%20is%20very%20family-friendly%2C%20with%20plenty%20of%20activities%20for%20kids%20to%20participate%20in.%3Cp%3EClea%20Barry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20I%20appreciate%20is%20that%20the%20school%20has%20club%20activities%2C%20like%20swimming%20and%20soccer%2C%20for%20the%20kids.%20Back%20in%20the%20US%2C%20I%20often%20had%20to%20shuttle%20them%20from%20place%20to%20place%20for%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df6c247a-e30f-456f-b46c-6fba2e2f105c%5C%22%3EA%20family-friendly%20lifestyle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20slower%20pace%20of%20life%20has%20been%20great%20for%20our%20family.%20On%20the%20weekends%2C%20we%20enjoy%20hiking%20together%20and%20going%20out%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-early-chiang-mai-thailand-slow-life-financial-security-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elove%20about%20Chiang%20Mai%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20its%20play%20caf%C3%A9s%20%E2%80%94%20restaurants%20with%20built-in%20play%20areas%20or%20activities%20for%20kids.%20So%20much%20of%20the%20dining%20here%20is%20outdoors%2C%20which%20means%20the%20kids%20get%20to%20run%20around.%20It%20almost%20feels%20like%20stepping%20back%20into%20the%20'90s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20feels%20safe%20here%2C%20and%20we%20feel%20comfortable%20letting%20the%20kids%20have%20a%20bit%20more%20independence.%20My%20daughter%2C%20now%20a%20tween%2C%20likes%20to%20go%20to%20the%20mall%20and%20meet%20her%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20coffee%20shop.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d42312ab5f9757add75e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShe%20says%20living%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%20has%20enabled%20her%20to%20enjoy%20her%20kids'%20childhoods%20more.%3Cp%3EClea%20Barry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20been%20very%20easy%20for%20us%20to%20find%20our%20community%2C%20especially%20through%20the%20school%20and%20through%20social%20media%20groups.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20events%20happening%20every%20weekend%20in%20Chang%20Mai%2C%20you%20almost%20have%20to%20pick%20and%20choose%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20work%20remotely%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20work%20as%20many%20hours%20as%20I%20used%20to.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20I%20only%20had%20a%20few%20weeks%20of%20vacation%20each%20year%20and%20didn't%20have%20summers%20off%2C%20which%20made%20family%20travel%20much%20harder.%20Since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-nomad-remote-work-chiang-mai-thailand-southeast-asia-easy-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoving%20to%20Chiang%20Mai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20travel%20to%2010%20different%20countries%20together%2C%20including%20Laos%20and%20Vietnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20been%20nice%20is%20that%20we've%20had%20a%20lot%20more%20time%20together.%20I'm%20able%20to%20enjoy%20my%20children's%20childhoods%20more%2C%20and%20that's%20something%20I'm%20really%20grateful%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-moved-from-america-to-thailand-chiang-mai-young