20beverages%20alongside%20our%20core%20coffee%20offerings%2C%26quot%3B%20Dana%20Pellicano%2C%20Starbucks'%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20global%20product%20experience%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20said%20Refreshers%20are%20helping%20drive%20growth%20in%20afternoon%20visits%2C%20an%20area%20the%20company%20has%20increasingly%20focused%20on%20as%20it%20seeks%20new%20sources%20of%20traffic.%20It%20sees%20customization%20as%20a%20key%20reason%20for%20the%20platform's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20reflects%20a%20broader%20shift%20underway%20across%20the%20restaurant%20industry%2C%20as%20chains%20compete%20not%20only%20with%20each%20other%20but%20also%20with%20energy%20drinks%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffunctional-drink-boom-wellness-arms-race-fiber-protein-adaptogens-nootropics-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efunctional%20beverages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20social-media-fueled%20drink%20trends%20for%20younger%20consumers'%20attention%20and%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20Refreshers%20first%20launched%20in%202012%2C%20we've%20seen%20increased%20interest%20in%20drinks%20that%20are%20flavor-forward%2C%20visually%20compelling%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20personalize%2C%26quot%3B%20Pellicano%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChains%20are%20no%20longer%20just%20competing%20with%20each%20other%20for%20coffee%20occasions%2C%26quot%3B%20Noah%20Pozin%2C%20a%20food%2C%20agribusiness%2C%20and%20beverage%20industry%20consultant%20at%20Truist%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20competing%20with%20energy%20drink%20brands%2C%20bottled%20teas%2C%20functional%20waters%2C%20and%20customized%20soda%20concepts%20for%20the%20broader%20'cold%2C%20caffeinated%2C%20customizable%20treat'%20occasion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224507f819-e716-47e5-a6d0-016ca921a3aa%5C%22%3EChasing%20younger%20tastes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDutch%20Bros%20has%20expanded%20its%20energy-drink%20offerings%2C%20which%20executives%20say%20now%20account%20for%20about%2025%25%20of%20its%20business.%20Customized%20soda%20chains%20have%20also%20surged%20in%20popularity%2C%20and%20restaurant%20brands%20from%20McDonald's%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyum-brands-earnings-trends-gen-z-tastes-taco-bell-kfc-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETaco%20Bell%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20investing%20heavily%20in%20cold%20beverages.%20Analysts%20at%20JPMorgan%20and%20KeyBanc%20have%20pointed%20to%20a%20growing%20pipeline%20of%20innovation%20from%20both%20Starbucks%20and%20Dutch%20Bros%20as%20chains%20race%20to%20capture%20demand%20for%20customizable%2C%20functional%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20what's%20driving%20that%20demand%20is%20a%20shift%20in%20how%20younger%20consumers%20think%20about%20beverages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-driving-fast-food-beverage-wars-demand-custom-drinks-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20and%20millennials%3C%2Fa%3E%20treat%20beverages%20more%20like%20personal%20expression%2C%20social%20content%2C%20functional%20fuel%2C%20and%20affordable%20indulgence%2C%26quot%3B%20Pozin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227486%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dutch%20Bros%20Myst%20Energy%20Refresher%20drinks%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2750d60421ca48aa59ffcc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225020%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStarbucks%20competitor%20Dutch%20Bros%20says%20customized%20energy%20drinks%2C%20such%20as%20its%20Myst%20Energy%20Refreshers%2C%20now%20account%20for%20roughly%2025%25%20of%20its%20business.%3Cp%3EIllustration%20by%20Mario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20younger%20consumers%20navigate%20persistent%20inflation%2C%20housing%20affordability%20challenges%2C%20and%20broader%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%20beverages%20have%20become%20a%20relatively%20accessible%20luxury%2C%20he%20said.%20Consumers%20are%20increasingly%20looking%20for%20opportunities%20to%20experiment%2C%20customize%2C%20and%20discover%20new%20products%20without%20making%20a%20major%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20trend%20has%20made%20beverages%20especially%20attractive%20to%20restaurant%20operators.%20Drinks%20typically%20carry%20higher%20margins%20than%20many%20food%20offerings%20and%20can%20help%20drive%20customer%20frequency%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20making%20them%20an%20increasingly%20important%20growth%20engine%20for%20chains%20seeking%20new%20revenue%20streams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20has%20only%20accelerated%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20insights%20for%20us%20has%20been%20just%20how%20creative%20customers%20are%20with%20Refreshers%2C%26quot%3B%20Pellicano%20said.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20early%20on%2C%20we%20saw%20customers%20take%20the%20core%20beverages%20and%20make%20them%20their%20own%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20that%20was%20swapping%20in%20coconut%20milk%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20Pink%20Drink%2C%20or%20layering%20in%20new%20flavors%2C%20textures%2C%20and%20colors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20started%20as%20customization%20quickly%20became%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPellicano%20said%20social%20media%20has%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Breal-time%20feedback%20loop%20and%20source%20of%20inspiration%26quot%3B%20for%20Starbucks%2C%20helping%20the%20company%20spot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-dirty-soda-refreshers-starbucks-dunkin-new-drinks-review-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eemerging%20drink%20trends%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20scale%20them%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20blended%20Refreshers%20arriving%20this%20summer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20additional%20innovations%20already%20in%20the%20pipeline%20%E2%80%94%20Starbucks%20is%20signaling%20that%20its%20future%20growth%20won't%20come%20solely