am%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-merging-codex-into-chatgpt-lock-in-code-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelease%20of%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20says%20the%20company%20is%20entering%20its%20third%20phase%20%E2%80%94%20making%20AI%20abundant%2C%20accessible%2C%20and%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Jakub%20Pachocki%2C%20OpenAI's%20chief%20scientist%2C%20published%20a%20blog%20post%20on%20Monday%20outlining%20their%20plan%20for%20the%20company.%20They%20said%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20OpenAI%20was%20about%20research%20toward%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%2C%20while%20the%20second%20was%20about%20offering%20their%20products%20to%20the%20world%20and%20learning%20how%20people%20actually%20use%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20we%20are%20entering%20the%20third%20phase%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20and%20Pachocki%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20economy%20is%20beginning%20to%20reshape%20around%20AI.%20The%20central%20question%20now%20is%20how%20to%20make%20advanced%20AI%20abundant%2C%20affordable%2C%20safe%2C%20useful%2C%20and%20easy%20enough%20for%20every%20person%20and%20organization%20to%20benefit%20from%20it.%20Frontier%20capability%20is%20only%20part%20of%20the%20job.%20The%20bigger%20task%20is%20turning%20that%20capability%20into%20tools%20people%20can%20actually%20use%20to%20thrive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20OpenAI%20has%20three%20main%20goals%3A%20to%20build%20an%20automated%20AI%20researcher%2C%20to%20accelerate%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20to%20give%20everyone%20on%20Earth%20a%20personal%20AGI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPowerful%20systems%20must%20remain%20safe%2C%20aligned%20with%20human%20intent%2C%20and%20subject%20to%20human%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BEntirely%20automating%20everything%20is%20not%20the%20future%20we%20want.%20It%20would%20be%20unfulfilling%2C%20and%20it%20would%20be%20dangerous.%20AI%20should%20help%20people%20pursue%20their%20goals%2C%20not%20become%20untethered%20from%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20said%20national%20and%20global%20coordination%20was%20needed%20and%20reiterated%20their%20call%20for%20an%20international%20organization%20that%20would%20work%20on%20reducing%20risks%20posed%20by%20AI%20and%20could%20slow%20down%20the%20development%20of%20frontier%20models%20if%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20good%20AI%20future%20cannot%20be%20one%20where%20a%20small%20number%20of%20institutions%20control%20most%20of%20the%20capability%20and%20most%20of%20the%20upside.%20It%20should%20be%20a%20future%20where%20many%20people%2C%20companies%2C%20communities%2C%20and%20countries%20can%20build%2C%20benefit%2C%20and%20hold%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20and%20Pachocki%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20came%20the%20same%20day%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-files-confidential-s-1-ipo-may-be-a-while-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20had%20confidentially%20filed%20for%20an%20initial%20public%20offering%2C%20though%20the%20company%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bmay%20be%20a%20while%26quot%3B%20before%20its%20stock%20actually%20hits%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20blog%20post%20was%20also%20reminiscent%20of%20one%20from%20another%20leading%20AI%20company%20eyeing%20an%20IPO.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-says-leading-ai-labs-may-need-to-hit-brakes-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearchers%20at%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20post%20last%20week%20that%20AI%20is%20advancing%20so%20quickly%20that%20leading%20frontier%20labs%20may%20need%20to%20slow%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20it%20would%20be%20good%20for%20the%20world%20to%20have%20the%20option%20to%20slow%20or%20temporarily%20pause%20frontier%20AI%20development%20to%20enable%20societal%20structures%20and%20alignment%20research%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20advance%20of%20the%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Fbuilt-to-benefit-everyone-our-plan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%20from%20OpenAI%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-third-phase-plan-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780958063000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a273d790421ca48aa59ffa7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-third-phase-plan-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20Sam%20Altman%20outlines%20AI's%20third%20phase%2C%20focusing%20on%20abundance%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20global%20collaboration%20as%20the%20company%20plans%20an%20IPO.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nuclear%20Arms%20Spending%20Hits%20Record%20High%2C%20China%20Leads%20Global%20Expansion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20and%20Russia%20together%20hold%20around%2083%20percent%20of%20the%20world's%20nuclear%20arms%20stockpile%2C%20with%20more%20than%205%2C000%20warheads%20each.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780957940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnuclear-arms-spending-hits-record-high-china-leads-global-expansion-11609857%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20and%20Russia%20together%20hold%20around%2083%20percent%20of%20the%20world's%20nuclear%20arms%20stockpile%2C%20with%20more%20than%205%2C000%20wa