Ford%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20Apple-focused%20accounts%20on%20social%20media%20celebrated%20the%20news%20while%20also%20lamenting%20that%20many%20owners%20of%20older%20Apple%20Watch%20models%20would%20be%20left%20out%20for%20watchOS%2027%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Apple%20Watch%20Series%209%2C%20first%20sold%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20Pixel%204%20and%204%20XL%2C%20and%20Samsung's%20Galaxy%20S10%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.androidauthority.com%2Fapple-ios-27-iphone-11-support-3675625%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Android%20Authority%2C%20both%20released%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20iPhone%2011%2C%20received%20just%203%20years%20of%20platform%20updates.%20With%20Monday's%20news%2C%20the%20iPhone%2011%20is%20set%20to%20receive%20seven%20years%20of%20major%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20older%20iPhones%20will%20get%20all%20the%20bells%20and%20whistles%20of%20the%20new%20iOS%2C%20especially%20the%20revamped%20Siri%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-new-siri-ai-chatbot-app-wwdc-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efinally%20brings%20more%20robust%20AI-enabled%20features%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Apple's%20virtual%20assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20said%20that%20to%20access%20those%20improvements%2C%20customers%20will%20need%20an%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20or%20Pro%20Max%2C%20or%20an%20iPhone%2016%20or%20later.%20And%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20most%20advanced%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%2C%20including%20a%20new%20Siri%20voice%20experience%2C%20an%20iPhone%20Air%2C%20iPhone%2017%20Pro%2C%20or%20later%20models%20will%20be%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-iphone-cpu-scheduler-older-models-11-support-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780957339000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https