6.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20star%20of%20the%20show%20was%20the%20new%20AI-powered%20Siri%20chatbot%2C%20part%20of%20Apple's%20new%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20keynote%20marked%20Tim%20Cook's%20final%20WWDC%20as%20Apple%20CEO.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-new-siri-ai-chatbot-app-wwdc-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple's%20AI%20era%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20taking%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20iPhone%20maker%20held%20its%20Worldwide%20Developers%20Conference%20%E2%80%94%20the%20annual%20event%20that%20offers%20developers%2C%20customers%2C%20and%20investors%20a%20road%20map%20for%20the%20company's%20future%20product%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20conference%20previewed%20software%20coming%20next%20to%20the%20iPhone%2C%20Mac%2C%20iPad%2C%20Apple%20Watch%2C%20and%20Vision%20Pro.%20The%20keynote%20also%20carried%20extra%20weight%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Ftim-cook%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETim%20Cook's%3C%2Fa%3E%20final%20time%20hosting%20WWDC%20as%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20biggest%20takeaways%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple's%3C%2Fa%3E%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEverything%20is%20AI%2C%20AI%2C%20AI%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20view%20from%20Apple's%20Vision%20Pro%20wearable%20inside%20a%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2729865bcf40c28b6b05a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20highlighted%20AI%20dozens%20of%20times%20during%20the%20event.%3Cp%3EApple%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20was%20one%20phrase%20the%20company%20wanted%20people%20to%20remember%20from%20WWDC%202026%2C%20it%20was%20Apple%20Intelligence%2C%20its%20very%20Apple-y%20branding%20for%20its%20suite%20of%20AI%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20said%20its%20new%20AI%20software%2C%20which%20has%20undergone%20a%20broad%20overhaul%2C%20is%20being%20threaded%20through%20every%20product%20%E2%80%94%20including%20its%20phone-based%20digital%20assistant%20Siri%20and%20the%20Vision%20Pro%20wearable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiri%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20getting%20an%20AI%20glow-up%20(more%20on%20that%20below).%20Safari%20will%20be%20able%20to%20organize%20tabs%20by%20topic%2C%20monitor%20webpages%20for%20updates%2C%20and%20create%20custom%20extensions%20from%20a%20natural-language%20prompt.%20Messages%2C%20Mail%2C%20Calendar%2C%20Phone%2C%20Home%2C%20and%20Shortcuts%20are%20all%20getting%20new%20AI-powered%20features%20that%20will%20help%20users%20do%20tasks%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20truly%20helpful%20AI%20must%20be%20centered%20around%20you%20and%20your%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20Apple's%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20software%20engineering%2C%20Craig%20Federighi%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOwn%20an%20older%20iPhone%3F%20Good%20news%E2%80%A6%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Several%20people%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20a%20white%20screen%20that%20says%20%26quot%3BiPhone%2011.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2723c40421ca48aa59fee4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20said%20its%20latest%20update%20will%20serve%20mobile%20phones%20ranging%20back%20to%20the%20iPhone%2011.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20says%20iOS%2027%20is%20designed%20to%20make%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-iphone-cpu-scheduler-older-models-11-support-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaging%20devices%20feel%20more%20responsive.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStacey%20Ford%2C%20Apple's%20vice%20president%20of%20operating%20systems%20program%20management%2C%20said%20the%20company%20is%20bringing%20an%20optimized%20CPU%20scheduler%20to%20older%20mobile%20devices%2C%20going%20all%20the%20way%20back%20to%20the%20iPhone%2011.%20The%20system%20helps%20manage%20how%20the%20phone%20allocates%20computing%20power%20as%20users%20juggle%20different%20tasks%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFord%20said%20the%20software%20update's%20inclusion%20of%20older%20phones%20makes%20it%20%26quot%3Bavailable%20to%20more%20users%20than%20any%20iOS%20update%2C%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESiri%20gets%20the%20chatbot%20treatment%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20own%20app%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222742%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shot%20of%20the%20iPhone%20with%20Apple%20Maps%20and%20Siri's%20new%20AI%20capabilities%20on%20the%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2724600421ca48aa59fee7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESiri%20is%20getting%20an%20AI%20boost%2C%20Apple%20said.%3Cp%3EApple%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESiri%20is%20getting%20a%20much-needed%20makeover%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20largely%20powered%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20there%20are%20times%20when%20you%20expect%20more%20from%20Siri%2C%26quot%3B%20Mike%20Rockwell%2C%20Apple's%20VP%20of%20Siri%20engineering%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BSiri%20is%20now%20a%20profoundly%20more%20capable%20assistant%20that%20helps%20you%20find%20what%20you%20need%20and%20gets%20more%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiri's%20software%20will%20make%20the%20assistant%20more%20conversational%20and%20better%20able%20to%20handle%20multi-step%20requests%2C%20even%20in%20third-party%20apps.%20The%20new%20AI-enhanced%20Siri%20can%20answer%20follow-up%20questions%2C%20pull%20from%20personal%20context%20located%20on%20the%20device%2C%20understand%20what's%20on%20your%20active%20screen%2C%20and%20take%20actions%20across%20apps%20%E2%80%94%20like%20finding%20photos%20from%20a%20trip%20and%20adding%20them%20to%20a%20shared%20album.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20also%20giving%20Siri%20AI%20its%20own%20app%2C%20where%20users%20can%20revisit%20past%20conversations%20across%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EApple%20leans%20further%20into%20altering%20your%20photos%20with%20AI%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222816%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20iPhones%2C%20showing%20the%20camera's%20new%20AI%20capabilities%2C%20are%20on%20the%20picture%20editing%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a272d085bcf40c28b6b05d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221574%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20said%20it's%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20edit%20a%20user's%20photos.%3Cp%3EApple%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20wants%20to%20be%20an%20iPhone%20user's%20photographic%20editor.%20The%20photo%20app%20has%20three%20new%20tools%20to%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhotos%20is%20getting%20an%20upgraded%20Clean%20Up%20tool%2C%20which%20removes%20distractions%20even%20in%20busy%20images%3B%20Extend%2C%20which%20can%20generate%20more%20images%20around%20the%20original%20frame%3B%20and%20Spatial%20Reframing%2C%20which%20lets%20users%20shift%20the%20perspective%20as%20if%20they%20had%20moved%20the%20camera%20before%20taking%20the%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20says%20the%20tools%20are%20meant%20to%20improve%20composition%2C%20not%20rewrite%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Apple%2C%20we%20have%20a%20deep%20respect%20for%20the%20craft%20of%20photography%2C%26quot%3B%20Alok%20Deshpande%2C%20Apple's%20director%20of%20photo%20and%20camera%20software%20engineering%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20goal%20for%20bringing%20AI%20into%20the%20Photos%20app%20is%20to%20help%20photographers%20enhance%20their%20images%20in%20ways%20that%20respect%20the%20original%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESorry%2C%20Apple%20fans%20in%20China%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20%E2%80%94%20you'l%20have%20to%20wait%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227876%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Customers%20shop%20in%20an%20Apple%20store%20in%20China.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a271fbb6f4f6ea1de4d360c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225251%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20said%20that%20Chinese%20and%20European%20iPhone%20users%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20access%20the%20new%20software%20initially.%3Cp%3ECheng%20Xin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20laying%20out%20all%20the%20benefits%20of%20Siri%20AI%2C%20Federighi%20shared%20the%20catch%3A%20users%20in%20the%20EU%20and%20China%20will%20find%20their%20access%20restricted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20cited%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-eu-official-visa-ban-big-tech-regulation-digital-service-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDigital%20Markets%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20restriction%2C%20and%20said%20that%20it%20had%20spent%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20months%26quot%3B%20proposing%20solutions%20that%20EU%20regulators%20have%20rejected.%20Users%20in%20the%20EU%20will%20be%20able%20to%20use%20Siri%20AI%20on%20their%20Macs%2C%20but%20not%20on%20their%20phones%20or%20watches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20working%20hard%20to%20find%20a%20path%20forward%20that%20preserves%20our%20users'%20privacy%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Federighi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20riding%20high%20for%20much%20of%20WWDC%2C%20Apple's%20stock%20sank%20following%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EParents%3A%20Your%20oversight%20powers%20are%20leveling%20up%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20iPhone%20from%20a%20parent%20user.%20It%20asks%20whether%20a%20parent%20wants%20to%20approve%20or%20decline%20a%20child's%20potential%20app%20download.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a272a990421ca48aa59ff13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222743%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20said%20its%20parental%20controls%20will%20let%20guardians%20approve%20or%20decline%20a%20child's%20app%20downloads.%3Cp%3EApple%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20expanding%20its%20protections%20for%20child%20accounts%2C%20introducing%20restrictions%20on%20how%20long%20your%20child%20can%20use%20their%20device%20and%20what%20they%20can%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParents%20can%20now%20instruct%20their%20child%20to%20request%20website%20access%20before%20browsing%2C%20or%20to%20request%20to%20text%20someone%20before%20messaging.%20They%20can%20also%20set%20time%20allowances%20for%20apps%20and%20restrict%20access%20during%20certain%20times%20of%20day%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-school-teacher-all-schools-should-ban-phones-in-classroom-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschool%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20wanting%20an%20immediate%20shutdown%2C%20parents%20now%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bpause%20device%26quot%3B%20button.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20those%20under%20the%20age%20of%2013%2C%20access%20to%20personal%20devices%20should%20be%20limited%20and%20expanded%20when%20a%20child%20is%20ready%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sumbul%20Ahmad%20Desai%2C%20Apple's%20VP%20of%20Health.%20%26quot%3BAs%20parents%2C%20we%20want%20our%20kids%20to%20develop%20healthy%20digital%20habits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHate%20Apple's%20Liquid%20Glass%20design%20theme%3F%20There's%20now%20a%20slider%20for%20that%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222866%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screen%20showing%20an%20Apple%20Music%20webpage%20with%20Apple's%20updated%20liquid%20glass%20design.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a272d6c5bcf40c28b6b05da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221592%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20is%20introducing%20new%20updates%20to%20its%20liquid%20glass%20design.%20Users%20can%20now%20toggle%20the%20opacity.%3Cp%3EApple%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year's%20WWDC%20brought%20a%20new%20%26quot%3BLiquid%20Glass%26quot%3B%20interface%20to%20Apple's%20screens.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-liquid-glass-iphone-upgrades-wall-street-analysts-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENot%20everyone%20loved%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20rolling%20out%20the%20glossy%20design%20language%20last%20year%2C%20Apple%20said%20it%20is%20making%20tweaks%20to%20improve%20readability%20and%20make%20apps%20feel%20more%20structured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20company%20isn't%20letting%20users%20fully%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20fresh%20look%2C%20a%20new%20settings%20slider%20lets%20users%20adjust%20Liquid%20Glass%20from%20ultra%20clear%20to%20fully%20tinted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETim%20Cook%20reflected%20on%20his%20final%20WWDC%20as%20CEO%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223844%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tim%20Cook's%20hands%20are%20pressed%20together%20as%20he%20talks%20onstage%20during%20the%202026%20Apple%20Worldwide%20Developers%20Conference.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2718165bcf40c28b6b0515%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222771%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECEO%20Tim%20Cook%2C%20who%20is%20stepping%20down%20in%20September%2C%20expressed%20gratitude%20during%20Monday's%20WWDC.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20Cook's%20final%20WWDC%20as%20Apple's%20top%20boss.%20He'll%20make%20way%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-apple-ceo-john-ternus-challenges-ai-talent-new-products-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJohn%20Ternus%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20take%20over%20as%20Apple's%20CEO%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%20ended%20the%20conference%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20note