us%20people%20spotted%20at%20the%20NBA%20Finals%20so%20far.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20also%20announced%20his%20plans%20to%20attend%20Game%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b508430d-7e3c-45dd-85de-822d2aa63539%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Results%5C%22%3EWho%20won%20the%20first%20two%20games%20of%20the%20NBA%20Finals%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Knicks%20won%20the%20first%20two%20games%20of%20the%20NBA%20Finals%2C%20despite%20San%20Antonio's%20home-court%20advantage.%20The%20Knicks%20won%20Game%201%20105-95%2C%20but%20Game%202%20was%20much%20tighter.%20The%20Spurs%20almost%20clawed%20their%20way%20back%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20but%20the%20Knicks%20ultimately%20pulled%20off%20a%20105-104%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d054e66-45ef-4dda-9b89-a7ddb594884f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Odds%5C%22%3EWho%20is%20favored%20to%20win%20Spurs%20vs.%20Knicks%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Knicks%20are%20currently%20the%20favorites%20to%20win%20both%20Game%203%20and%20the%20overall%20NBA%20Finals.%20Ahead%20of%20Game%203%20(at%20the%20time%20of%20writing)%2C%20DraftKings%20has%20the%20Knicks%20as%201.5-point%20favorites%20and%20-130%20on%20the%20moneyline%2C%20while%20the%20Spurs%20are%20the%20%2B110%20underdogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289cb1757-cc32-433e-b494-d15a9829367d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Schedule%5C%22%3ENBA%20Finals%20schedule%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGame%201%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20June%203%20at%208%3A30%20p.m.%20ET%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGame%202%20on%20Friday%2C%20June%205%20at%208%3A30%20p.m.%20ET%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGame%203%20on%20Monday%2C%20June%208%20at%208%3A30%20p.m.%20ET%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGame%204%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20June%2010%20at%208%3A30%20p.m.%20ET%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGame%205%20on%20Saturday%2C%20June%2013%20at%208%3A30%20p.m.%20ET%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGame%206%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20June%2016%20at%208%3A30%20p.m.%20ET%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGame%207%20on%20Friday%2C%20June%2019%20at%208%