2C%20is%20laying%20off%20employees%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20email%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-orb-eye-scanning-startup-billion-user-goal-viability-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruggled%20to%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20its%20iris-scanning%20%26quot%3BOrb%26quot%3B%20can%20generate%20revenue%20and%20win%20over%20regulators%2C%20despite%20a%20%242.5%20billion%20valuation%20and%20millions%20of%20sign-ups.%20Investors%20like%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%2C%20Bain%20Capital%2C%20and%20Khosla%20Ventures%20have%20poured%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20into%20the%20venture%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20enter%20the%20next%20step%20of%20our%20company%20strategy%20and%20operating%20priorities%2C%20we%20have%20made%20the%20hard%20decision%20to%20make%20changes%20to%20some%20roles%20and%20teams%20across%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Tools%20for%20Humanity%20said%20in%20the%20email%2C%20which%20was%20sent%20to%20staffers%20Monday%20from%20the%20people%20team.%20The%20company%20will%20share%20details%20on%20its%20strategy%20and%20next%20steps%20in%20a%20town%20hall%20meeting%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20email%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20many%20employees%20would%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20layoffs.%20Tools%20for%20Humanity%20employs%20more%20than%20500%20people%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toolsforhumanity.com%2Fcareers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20company%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETools%20for%20Humanity%20was%20founded%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20iris%20scans%20to%20prove%20a%20person%20is%20human%20and%20not%20an%20AI%20bot.%20The%20startup's%20Orb%E2%80%94a%20shiny%2C%20volleyball-sized%20sphere%E2%80%94scans%20irises%20to%20generate%20a%20digital%20ID.%20People%20who%20participate%20can%20receive%20tokens%20of%20Worldcoin%2C%20a%20cryptocurrency%20distributed%20by%20the%20Cayman%20Island-based%20World%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Tools%20for%20Humanity%20or%20have%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aneinbinder%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eneinbinder%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20neinbinder.70.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20device%2C%20and%20nonwork%20WiFi%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecure-news-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-orb-worldcoin-tools-for-humanity-layoffs-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780952727000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a272c3e0421ca48aa59ff18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-orb-worldcoin-tools-for-humanity-layoffs-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tools%20for%20Humanity%20has%20struggled%20to%20show%20how%20its%20iris-scanning%20%26quot%3BOrb%26quot%3B%20can%20generate%20revenue.%20Now%20it's%20laying%20off%20employees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22neinbinder%40businessinsider.com%20(Nicole%20Einbinder)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20mega-IPO%20wave%20led%20by%20SpaceX%20and%20Anthropic%20has%20retirees%20worried%20about%20their%20finances.%20Their%20advisors%20say%20otherwise.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221753%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20SpaceX%20rocket%20firing%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0f25c151ede568c7e16fd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20SpaceX%20IPO%20will%20not%20drastically%20impact%20most%20retirees'%20portfolios.%3Cp%3ESpaceX%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUpcoming%20IPOs%20for%20companies%20like%20SpaceX%20and%20Anthropic%20have%20some%20retirees%20worried.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20overall%20agree%20that%20these%20IPOs%20may%20have%20limited%20immediate%20impact%20on%20401(k)s.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Nasdaq%20100%20and%20Russell%201000%20are%20expected%20to%20include%20SpaceX%20relatively%20soon%20after%20going%20public.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERetirees%20may%20have%20questions%20about%20huge%2C%20soon-to-be%20public%20companies%20like%20SpaceX%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20coming%20to%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-retirement-plans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretirement%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20despite%20all%20the%20attention%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshould-i-buy-spacex-ipo-investing-advice-elon-musk-spcx-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einitial%20public%20offerings%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20getting%2C%20the%20first%20lesson%20for%20most%20people%20with%20retirement%20accounts%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Findex-fund-vs-mutual-fund%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindex%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20simple%3A%20these%20new%20stocks%20are%20unlikely%20to%20make%20a%20big%2C%20immediate%20difference%20in%20their%20retirement%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20most%20retirement%20accounts%20are%20built%20around%20mutual%20funds%20and%20ETFs%20that%20track%20broad%20indexes%2C%20and%20those%20indexes%20don't%20usually%20snap%20up%20a%20new%20company%20at%20its%20full%20market%20value%20the%20moment%20it%20goes%20public.%20Instead%2C%20they%20often%20rely%20on%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-anthropic-openai-stock-spcx-ai-index-026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efree%20float%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20shares%20actually%20available%20to%20public%20investors%20%E2%80%94%20and%20weight%20new%20stocks%20gradually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIPOs%20don't%20meaningfully%20move%20retirement%20portfolios%20right%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rodney%20Comegys%2C%20chief%20information%20officer%20and%20head%20of%20global%20equity%20at%20Vanguard%20Capital%20Management.%20%26quot%3BDue%20to%20float-adjusted%20indexing%2C%20even%20mega%20IPOs%20will%20enter%20broad%20indexes%20at%20very%20small%20weights%2C%20so%20the%20near-term%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F401k-hardship-withdrawals-record-retirement-savings-investment-accounts-stock-market-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimpact%20on%20401(k)s%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20limited.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nasdaq%20100%20and%20Russell%201000%20are%20expected%20to%20include%20these%20giants%20relatively%20soon%20after%20they%20go%20public.%20SpaceX%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-why-retail-investor-push-raises-red-flags-musk-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reportedly%20pushed%20indexes%20to%20allow%20SpaceX%20to%20trade%20within%20days%2C%20anticipating%20a%20strong%20performance.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20a%20holdout%2C%20blocking%20SpaceX%20for%20at%20least%2012%20months%20after%20declining%20to%20amend%20proposed%20rule%20changes%20that%20would%20have%20sped%20its%20entry%20to%20the%20benchmark%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20prominent%20financial%20experts%20have%20called%20SpaceX's%20targeted%20valuation%20of%20%241.8%20trillion%20too%20high.%20Morningstar%20valued%20the%20aerospace%20manufacturer%20at%20%24780%20billion%2C%20citing%20revenue%20gaps%20and%20AI%20risks%2C%20while%20%26quot%3BDean%20of%20Valuation%26quot%3B%20and%20NYU%20professor%20Aswath%20Damodaran%20put%20it%20at%20%241.3%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20holders%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-troubles-retirement-funds-401k-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretirement%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20will%20soon%20allow%20SpaceX%20to%20begin%20trading%2C%20this%20uncertainty%20could%20mean%20greater%20risk%20and%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20financial%20advisors%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20retirees%20often%20don't%20know%20what's%20in%20their%20401(k)s%20and%20are%20thus%20unlikely%20to%20reduce%20their%20tech%20exposure.%20Still%2C%20the%20consensus%20is%20not%20to%20worry%20much%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20number%20of%20shares%20available%20to%20the%20public%20will%20be%20limited%20at%20first%20until%20more%20stock%20is%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EU.S.%20households%20aged%2065%20or%20older%20made%20up%20the%20largest%20age%20cohort%20with%20zero%20retirement%20savings%2C%20as%20of%20the%202022%20Survey%20of%20Consumer%20Finances%2C%20meaning%20these%20IPOs%20will%20affect%20many%20older%20Americans%20the%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20many%20of%20these%20funds%20counter%20big%20moves%20in%20large-cap%20companies%20via%20diversification%2C%20holding%20stable%20assets%20like%20bonds%20to%20offset%20big%20swings%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMikel%20Van%20Cleve%2C%20advice%20director%20of%20retirement%20and%20complex%20planning%20at%20USAA%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20while%20diversification%20retains%20the%20strength%20of%20index%20investing%2C%20portfolio%20exposures%20shift%20over%20time%2C%20which%20may%20prompt%20investors%20to%20adjust%20their%20risk%20tolerance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20behavioral%20finance%20standpoint%2C%20the%20challenge%20is%20that%20many%20investors%20associate%20index%20funds%20with%20being%20broadly%20diversified%20and%20inherently%20conservative%2C%20without%20always%20recognizing%20how%20index%20composition%20can%20evolve%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Van%20Cleve%20said.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20periods%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feveryone-is-building-everything-openai-anthropic-lovable-cursor-canva-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcitement%20around%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20innovation%2C%20that%20can%20contribute%20to%20overconfidence%20and%20elevated%20return%20expectations%2C%20while%20periods%20of%20volatility%20can%20trigger%20fear-based%20reactions%20or%20reactive%20decision-making.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarcus%20Sturdivant%20Sr.%2C%20of%20The%20ABC%20Squared%2C%20a%20Registered%20Investment%20Advisory%20firm%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20retirees%20may%20be%20shielded%20from%20the%20impact%20of%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-spcx-stock-elon-musk-investing-market-retail-investors-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpaceX%20in%20their%20401(k)s%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20the%20stock%20won't%20be%20included%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20if%20it%20had%20been%20included%20in%20%5Bthe%20index%5D%2C%20retirees%20would%20have%20been%20screwed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20there%20are%20going%20to%20be%20plenty%20of%20retirees%20who%20actually%20want%20this%20stock%20in%20spite%20of%20the%2095%20to%20100%20times%20earnings%2C%20just%20because%20they%20know%20Tesla.%20I%20can%20definitely%20see%20retirees%20not%20particularly%20minding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20specifically%2C%20he%20thinks%20those%20with%20years%20before%20retirement%20may%20not%20mind%20SpaceX%20exposure%2C%20but%20those%20who%20plan%20on%20cashing%20in%20their%20401(k)s%20soon%20will%20likely%20be%20more%20worried%20about%20short-term%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20about%20to%20retire%2C%20you%20probably%20don't%20want%20it%20there%2C%20but%20if%20you've%20got%20the%20horizon%2C%20it's%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20buying%20SpaceX%20stock%3F%20Are%20you%20an%20older%20American%20with%20thoughts%20about%20how%20upcoming%20IPOs%20may%20impact%20your%20portfolio%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20nsheidlower%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-retirement-401k-portfolio-ai-elon-musk-anthropic-openai-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780952463000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2720ec5bcf40c28b6b0577%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-retirement-401k-portfolio-ai-elon-musk-anthropic-openai-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IPOs%20for%20companies%20like%20SpaceX%20and%20Anthropic%20have%20some%20retirees%20worried%2C%20but%20experts%20overall%20agree%20these%20IPOs%20will%20have%20limited%20impact%20on%20401(k)s.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nsheidlower%40businessinsider.com%20(Noah%20Sheidlower%2CSamuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Twitch%20streamer%20Kathelina%E2%80%99s%20controversy%20deepens%20as%20former%20best%20friend%20Snowcone%20speaks%20out%20after%20Kenneth%E2%80%99s%20cheating%20allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780952400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131596813%2Cimgsize-25206.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Ftwitch-streamer-kathelinas-controversy-deepens-as-former-best-friend-s