0in%20her%20life%20at%20sea.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20and%20condensed%20for%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyacht-stewardess-florida-earns-5000-month-travel-careers-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyachting%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%20young%20and%20worked%20my%20way%20up.%20Along%20the%20way%2C%20I%20worked%20for%20some%20extraordinary%20owners%20who%20taught%20me%20a%20lot%20about%20being%20a%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20once%20working%20for%20this%20one%20owner%20and%20hearing%20him%20on%20the%20phone%20in%20his%20office.%20He%20was%20dealing%20with%20his%20boat%20and%20he%20goes%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%2C%20take%2015%20minutes%20and%20educate%20me.%26quot%3B%20And%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EHe%20doesn't%20know!%20Wow%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20know%20everything.%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20That%20was%20a%20big%20learning%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20captain%20and%20leader%20on%20board%2C%20my%20biggest%20challenge%20is%20keeping%20consistency%20with%20the%20crew.%20No%20owner%20or%20client%20wants%20to%20go%20through%20different%20crew%20for%20repeat%20charters.%20It's%20like%20%26quot%3BCheers%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20you%20always%20go%20back%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhere%20people%20know%20who%20you%20are%2C%20right%3F%20They%20know%20your%20preferences%2C%20how%20you%20like%20your%20tea%20or%20how%20you%20take%20your%20coffee.%20We%20have%20logs%20where%20we%20keep%20tabs%20on%20our%20repeat%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Power%20Hours%20series%20gives%20readers%20an%20inside%20look%20at%20how%20powerful%20business%20leaders%20structure%20their%20workday.%20See%20more%20stories%20from%20the%20series%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpower-hours-day-in-the-life-successful-business-leaders-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20reach%20out%20to%20editor%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Flauryn-haas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3ELauryn%20Haas%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20your%20daily%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20superpower%20is%20that%20I'm%20good%20at%20leading%20crew%20so%20they%20come%20back.%20I%20don't%20lead%20with%20fear%20and%20I%20don't%20lead%20with%20intimidation.%20I%20lead%20like%20a%20puppy%3A%20If%20you've%20got%20a%20puppy%20and%20you%20want%20to%20teach%20them%20how%20to%20swim%2C%20you%20go%20swimming.%20The%20puppy's%20going%20to%20watch%20you%20on%20the%20steps.%20Next%20thing%20you%20know%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20crawl%20in%20that%20water%20and%20start%20swimming%20with%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20a%20typical%20day%20in%20my%20life%20at%20sea%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Captain%20Sandy%20Yawn%20wears%20a%20hat%20and%20sunglasses%20holding%20a%20radio%20on%20deck%20in%20Croatia.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2703a95bcf40c28b6b03ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaptain%20Sandy%20on%20season%2011%20of%20%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%20Mediterranean.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EFred%20Jagueneau%2FBravo%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22797e9119-e807-4de7-89f7-29c5956bd50d%5C%22%3EI'm%20on%20deck%20at%207%20a.m.%20and%20work%20out%20every%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20my%20routine%20on%20board%2C%20I'm%20on%20deck%20at%207%20a.m.%20and%20I'm%20there%20until%20the%20last%20person%20goes%20to%20bed.%20I%20try%20to%20get%20a%20rest%20period%20in%20the%20middle.%20We're%20required%20to%20have%20eight%20hours%20of%20rest%20in%20a%2024-hour%20period%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20maritime%20law%20%E2%80%94%20but%20how%20we%20choose%20to%20use%20our%20rest%20time%20is%20up%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20creature%20of%20habit.%20I%20like%20a%20good%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-time-drink-coffee-in-the-morning-2015-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoffee%20in%20the%20morning%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20not%20a%20morning%20eater%2C%20so%20I%20usually%20don't%20eat%20in%20the%20morning%20until%20about%2010%20or%2011%20a.m.%2C%20but%20I'll%20have%20fresh%20orange%20juice.%20When%20I'm%20home%20in%20Florida%2C%20I'll%20squeeze%20fresh%20orange%20juice%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20eat%20well%2C%20but%20filming%20this%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%20Mediterranean%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20ate%20a%20lot%20of%20croissants.%20I%20was%20there%20a%20week%20before%20filming%20started%2C%20and%20man%2C%20did%20I%20put%20some%20weight%20on.%20Thankfully%2C%20we%20had%20a%20gym%20in%20our%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20gym%20person.%20I%20like%20going%20where%20people%20are.%20At%20home%2C%20we%20have%20two%20SoulCycle%20bikes%20and%20a%20gym.%20I've%20been%20working%20out%20every%20day%20because%2C%20the%20older%20you%20get%2C%20the%20harder%20it%20is%20to%20stay%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf957d51-b159-463a-a310-20fc31977766%5C%22%3EMy%20routine%20and%20leadership%20style%20is%20influenced%20by%20my%20sobriety%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20sober.%20I%20have%20the%20magic%20of%20the%2012%20steps%2C%20which%20to%20me%20is%20life-changing%2C%20and%20I%20go%20to%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20morning%2C%20I'll%20read%20a%20meditation%2C%20and%20then%20I%20hit%20my%20knees%20and%20I%20ask%20for%20help%20for%20the%20day%20and%20ask%20to%20be%20a%20good%20human%20being%20and%20not%20selfish.%20And%20then%20I%20start%20my%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20my%20day%2C%20I%20review%20my%20day%2C%20because%20that's%20part%20of%20the%2012%20steps%2C%20too%3A%20Have%20I%20hurt%20anyone%3F%20Do%20I%20owe%20an%20amends%3F%20It's%20the%20maintenance%20part%20of%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20never%20forget%2C%20once%2C%20I%20had%20a%20phone%20call%20in%20my%20cabin%20with%20the%20boat's%20owner.%20It%20was%20about%20money%2C%20the%20budget%20%E2%80%94%20I'd%20gone%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eover.%20I%20come%20out%2C%20and%20my%20first%20officer%20asks%20me%20a%20question.%20I%20bit%20his%20head%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20at%20his%20face%2C%20and%20he%20went%20from%20happy%20to%20sad%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20God%2C%20I%20love%20this%20guy.%20He's%20such%20a%20great%20guy.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20make%20him%20sad.%26quot%3B%20So%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRob%2C%20you%20didn't%20deserve%20that.%20I'm%20sorry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aesha%20Scott%2C%20Cooper%20Dawson%2C%20Kayley%20Smith%2C%20Joe%20Bradley%2C%20and%20Captain%20Sandy%20Yawn%20on%20the%20dock%20on%20season%2011%20of%20%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%20Med.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a27044c5bcf40c28b6b03f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaptain%20Sandy%20with%20the%20crew%20of%20%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%20Mediterranean%26quot%3B%20season%2011.%3Cp%3EFred%20Jagueneau%2FBravo%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPromptly%20admitting%20when%20you've%20made%20a%20mistake%20and%20saying%20you're%20sorry%2C%20that's%20the%2010th%20step.%20Even%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbelow-deck-private-chef-what-charter-yacht-guests-should-know-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20with%20the%20crew%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20I%20say%20something%20that%20hurts%20someone's%20feelings%20or%20I'm%20not%20thinking%2C%20I'll%20apologize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b536b3f-2b2b-4da4-bd5e-9ce24346da31%5C%22%3EYachting%20keeps%20me%20away%20from%20home%2C%20but%20not%20as%20much%20as%20it%20used%20to%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20maritime%20industry%20has%20evolved%20since%20I%20started.%20Before%2C%20when%20we%20worked%2C%20people%20didn't%20see%20me%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20there%20when%20my%20mom%20died.%20I%20wasn't%20in%20her%20life%20for%20two%20years.%20I'd%20talk%20to%20her%2C%20but%20I%20hadn't%20seen%20her.%20That%20was%20terrible%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BSomething%20has%20to%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20has%20changed%20since%20then.%20Now%2C%20you%20get%20these%20rotations%20on%20these%20bigger%20boats.%20Some%20crew%20may%20get%20four%20months%20or%20five%20months%20on%2C%20five%20months%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-below-deck-med-cast-crew-luxury-yacht-bahamas-boyfriend-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebetween%20%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20I'll%20run%20a%20few%20boats.%20It%20isn't%20like%20charters%2C%20because%20to%20run%20a%20charter%2C%20the%20owner%20wants%20to%20hire%20you.%20And%20I'm%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI've%20got%20to%20go%20do%20this%20TV%20show%2C%20sorry!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bc074a93-2e54-4849-9d9e-5270487e8b67%5C%22%3EFilming%20'Below%20Deck'%20is%20a%20whirlwind%2C%20and%20I%20arrive%20early%20to%20adjust.%20At%20the%20end%2C%20my%20wife%20visits%20me.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFilming%20%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20intense%20than%20a%20typical%20yacht%20season.%20We%20are%20in%20it%20until%20it's%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20chartering%2C%20you%20usually%20have%20more%20time%20in%20between%20charters%2C%20so%20you%20get%20a%20longer%20break%20to%20recharge%20your%20batteries.%20Here%2C%20you're%20back-to-back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20listen%2C%20I've%20done%20back-to-back%20charters%20and%2024-hour%20turnarounds%20in%20my%20career%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20with%20brown%20hair%20sits%20across%20a%20table%20from%20a%20woman%20with%20blonde%20hair%20smilling.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26fca05bcf40c28b6b0396%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaptain%20Sandy%20with%20her%20wife%2C%20Leah%20Rae%20Yawn%2C%20on%20%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%20Mediterranean.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EFred%20Jagueneau%2FBravo%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I'm%20filming%20%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20wife%20Leah%20comes%20out%20to%20see%20me%20at%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFilming%20is%20six%20weeks%2C%20and%20I'm%20gone%20for%20eight%20weeks.%20I%20go%20early%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20time%20zone.%20I'm%20taking%20on%20a%20boat%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20with%20a%20whole%20new%20crew%20%E2%80%94%20I%20need%20at%20least%20four%20days%20to%20prepare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2240946b7c-e24f-4fa3-8d94-4a973be15299%5C%22%3EI%20prefer%20in-person%20and%20phone%20conversations%20to%20emails%20and%20texts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20on%20deck%20is%20about%20speaking%20clearly.%20We%20learn%20in%20maritime%20school%20how%20to%20project%20our%20voices.%20We%20have%20to%20be%20crisp%20in%20our%20communication.%20Our%20enunciation%20and%20pronunciation%20have%20to%20be%20spot-on.%20We%20practice%20in%20a%20classroom%20how%20to%20talk%20on%20a%20radio%20and%20ask%20for%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20talking%20softly%2C%20people%20are%20not%20going%20to%20listen.%20If%20you're%20talking%20too%20harshly%2C%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20listen.%20But%20if%20you%20talk%20in%20a%20way%20that's%20inviting%20and%20invigorating%20and%20direct%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20listen%20because%20it's%20almost%20like%20a%20respect%20of%20that.%20So%20your%20voice%20is%20everything.%20Your%20voice%20is%20your%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Victoria%20%26quot%3BV%26quot%3B%20San%20Juan%20and%20Captain%20Sandy%20Yawn%20stand%20on%20the%20bridge%20of%20a%20yacht%20on%20%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%20Med.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2704fa5bcf40c28b6b0400%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaptain%20Sandy%20with%20a%20crew%20member%20on%20season%2010%20of%20%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%20Mediterranean.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EFred%20Jagueneau%2FBravo%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20say%20to%20my%20friend%20who%20runs%20a%20charity%20and%20works%20a%20lot%20on%20email%2C%20%26quot%3BPick%20the%20phone%20up.%26quot%3B%20You've%20got%20to%20have%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20start%20seeing%20more%20than%20two%2C%20three%2C%20or%20four%20texts%20going%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20I%20pick%20the%20phone%20up.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20gets%20escalated%20in%20your%20mind.%20You%20might%20think%20the%20tone's%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f65c5c98-efa1-4035-b9e2-d9cc0c6ef336%5C%22%3EAt%20home%20and%20off-charter%2C%20I%20like%20traveling%20and%20seeing%20live%20music%20with%20my%20wife%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20I%20said%20to%20Leah%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20having%20fun.%20We%20work%20too%20much.%20We're%20working%20all%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%20I'm%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20see%20some%20live%20music%2C%20take%20some%20dance%20lessons%20with%20you.%20%26quot%3B%20So%20we'll%20do%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20with%20Southern%20rock%20and%20roll%2C%20but%20I%20like%20pop%20music.%20I%20like%20all%20of%20it.%20My%20playlist%20is%20very%20mixed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20got%20friends%20all%20over%20the%20place%2C%20and%20we'll%20travel%20to%20really%20nice%20places.%20I'm%20an%20experiences%20person.%20I%20want%20some%20nice%20clothes%2C%20of%20course%2C%20but%20I%20would%20rather%20spend%20money%20on%20experiences.%20So%20we'll%20go%20to%20the%20Monaco%20Boat%20Show.%20We're%20going%20to%20the%20Hamptons%20for%20a%20week%2C%20then%20we're%20going%20to%20go%20to%20Ne