s%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fkick-streamer-oblivions-family-mart-encounter-sparks-debate-over-livestream-etiquette-in-japan%2Famp_articleshow%2F131596623.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20went%20on%20my%20first%20adults-only%20cruise.%20From%20a%20playground%20to%20a%20tattoo%20shop%2C%20these%208%20things%20surprised%20me%20most.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222612%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Th%20author%20stands%20smiling%20in%20front%20of%20a%20docked%20cruise%20ship%20and%20smaller%20vessels%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fe9051a466d2b74ab33698%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221959%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20adults-only%20cruise%20with%20Virgin%20Voyages%20surprised%20Business%20Insider's%20reporter%20with%20sleek%20style%20and%20unique%20offerings.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20took%20my%20first%20adults-only%20cruise%20in%20August%202023%20with%20the%20luxury%20cruise%20line%20Virgin%20Voyages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20ship%20was%20full%20of%20surprises%2C%20including%20a%20tattoo%20parlor%20and%20a%20playground%20for%20grown-ups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20biggest%20surprise%20of%20my%20adults-only%20cruise%20was%20that%20it%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20a%20kid%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freasons-why-you-might-not-enjoy-caribbean-cruise-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20cruise%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20I%20didn't%20think%20the%20vacation%20style%20was%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20inaugural%20sailing%20aboard%C2%A0Royal%20Caribbean's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froyal-caribbean-wonder-of-the-seas-cruise-ship-tour%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWonder%20of%20the%20Seas%20%3C%2Fa%3Efelt%20like%20Kid%20Central.%20From%20the%20waterslides%20and%20splash%20pads%20to%20the%20carousel%20and%20escape%20room%2C%20many%20of%20the%20ship's%20activities%20and%20amenities%20were%20geared%20toward%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20more%20experienced%20cruisers%20might%20be%20able%20to%20tune%20them%20out%2C%20I%20found%20it%20tough%20to%20relax%20with%20kids%20running%20around%20screaming%20on%20the%20pool%20deck.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20give%20up%20cruising%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20I%20heard%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-voyages-scarlet-lady-back-to-back-cruise-adults-only-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVirgin%20Voyages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20luxury%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadults-only-cruise-virgin-voyages-vs-royal-caribbean%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadults-only%20cruise%3C%2Fa%3E%20line%20that%20first%20set%20sail%20in%202021.%20I%20thought%20sailing%20on%20an%20upscale%20ship%20free%20of%20children%20might%20change%20my%20mind%20about%20cruising%2C%20so%20I%20booked%20a%20seven-night%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-mediterranean-cruise-mistake-left-me-jet-lagged-for-days-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20cruise%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20August%202023%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-voyages-valiant-lady-cruise-ship-tour-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EVirgin%20Voyages'%20Valiant%20Lady%20ship%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20stayed%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-voyages-sea-terrace-room-balcony-photo-cruise-cabin-tour-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecabin%20with%20a%20balcony%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20starting%20rate%20was%20%245%2C910%2C%20though%20Business%20Insider%20received%20a%20media%20rate%20for%20the%20weeklong%20cruise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20second%20cruise%20was%20far%20better%20than%20my%20first.%20I%20sailed%20in%20peaceful%20luxury%20from%20Spain%20to%20Italy%20and%20France%2C%20and%20the%20ship%20was%20full%20of%20surprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20first%20thing%20that%20struck%20me%20was%20the%20ship's%20unique%20and%20alluring%20aesthetic.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside.%20a%20cruise%20ship%20lobby%20are%20white%20walls%20and%20a%20circular%20ceiling%20feature%20with%20blue%20and%20purple%20lights%20shining%20down%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de3b6a6080194819fa8fe3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ship%20was%20more%20stylish%20than%20I%20could%20have%20imagined.%20Multicolored%20lighting%2C%20iridescent%20panels%20paired%20with%20bold%20artwork%2C%20and%20modern%20furniture%20gave%20it%20a%20futuristic%20and%20glamorous%20feel.%20Pops%20of%20Virgin's%20signature%20bright%20red%20dotted%20the%20decks%2C%20from%20furniture%20to%20accent%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColorful%20glows%2C%20from%20pink%20and%20purple%20to%20blue%20and%20green%2C%20lit%20the%20decks%20and%20elevators.%20I%20felt%20as%20if%20I%20were%20surrounded%20by%20rainbows.%20Simply%20wandering%20the%20ship%20renewed%20my%20sense%20of%20childlike%20wonder%2C%20yet%20no%20kids%20were%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20cabin%20felt%20more%20spacious%20than%20I%20thought%20it%20would.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20the%20author%20sitting%20on%20a%20bed%20in%20a%20cruise%20ship%20cabin%20and%20standing%20on%20the%20cabin's%20balcony%20with%20the%20ocean%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fd40a4a466d2b74ab31ab8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20prepared%20for%20my%20225-square-foot%20cabin%20to%20feel%20at%20least%20a%20bit%20cramped%2C%20especially%20since%20I%20traveled%20with%20a%20friend.%20So%20I%20was%20surprised%20when%20multipurpose%20furniture%20and%20clever%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-small-space-storage-solutions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estorage%20hacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20left%20us%20both%20with%20enough%20floor%20space%20to%20stretch%20and%20move%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20queen-size%20bed%20transformed%20into%20a%20couch%20during%20the%20day%2C%20an%20ottoman%20was%20tucked%20underneath%20the%20desk%20instead%20of%20a%20chair%2C%20and%20the%20nightstand%20was%20thin%20and%20light%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20way%20when%20not%20in%20use.%20A%20large%20wall%20mirror%20facing%20the%20balcony%20made%20the%20space%20feel%20bigger%20and%20brighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20balcony%20had%20a%20side%20table%2C%20two%20chairs%2C%20and%20a%20big%2C%20netted%20hammock.%20Three%20years%20later%2C%20I%20still%20reminisce%20about%20how%20peaceful%20I%20felt%20curled%20up%20in%20that%20hammock%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20didn't%20expect%20to%20find%20a%20playground%20on%20a%20ship%20for%20grown-ups.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20empty%20deck%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship%20with%20a%20black%20seesaw%2C%20swings%2C%20and%20%20a%20red%20staircase%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6580b01e1c5c7b8c9a096c8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20thing%20I%20expected%20to%20find%20on%20an%20adults-only%20cruise%20ship%20was%20a%20playground.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20just%20any%20playground%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20was%20jumbo-sized%2C%20from%20the%20seesaws%20to%20the%20swings.%20It%20was%20clearly%20built%20for%20grown-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-voyages-adults-only-cruise-ship-playground-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecruise%20ship%20playground%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20filled%20with%20fun%20activities%2C%20including%20a%20human-sized%20chess%20set%2C%20a%20boxing%20ring%2C%20and%20gymnastics%20equipment.%20Nearby%2C%20a%20net%20suspended%20above%20an%20ocean%20view%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20on%20a%20catamaran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20had%20been%20children%20around%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20felt%20comfortable%20taking%20up%20space%20on%20this%20playground.%20I%20remember%20feeling%20weird%20as%20the%20only%20adult%20in%20a%20round%20of%20laser%20tag%20during%20my%20first%20cruise.%20But%20on%20this%20kid-free%20ship%2C%20I%20felt%20free%20to%20enjoy%20these%20activities%20surrounded%20by%20only%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20on%20the%20swings%20and%20playing%20competitive%20games%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20a%20kid%20again.%20Simply%20playing%20refreshed%20my%20state%20of%20mind%20in%20a%20way%20I%20didn't%20expect%2C%20and%20I%20think%20all%20adults%20could%20use%20it%20on%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20no%20shortage%20of%20play%20indoors%2C%20either.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20the%20author%20in%20sunglasses%20drives%20a%20car%20in%20an%20arcade%20with%20blue%20lighting%20behind%20her%20and%20a%20black%20shelf%20full%20of%20board%20games%20with%20wood%20floors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecdaf83c42320019c01ec5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20wanted%20to%20beat%20the%20heat%2C%20I%20headed%20inside%20on%20deck%20seven%2C%20where%20I%20found%20a%20retro-style%20arcade%20and%20a%20game%20room%20full%20of%20board%20games%2C%20puzzles%2C%20decks%20of%20cards%2C%20and%20large%20tables%20to%20play%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20game%20selection%20was%20nostalgic%20%E2%80%94%20I%20spotted%20childhood%20favorites%20like%20Mouse%20Trap%2C%20Candyland%2C%20and%20Cranium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20never%20thought%20I'd%20see%20a%20tattoo%20parlor%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tattoo%20parlor%20with%20red%20chairs%20and%20a%20port%20hole%20window%20with%20a%20view%20of%20the%20ocean%20on%20the%20right%20and%20a%20counter%20top%20and%20shelf%20on%20the%20left%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fd2ab3c6ad288d147e146a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EVirgin%20Voyages%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20wandering%20the%20indoor%20shopping%20strip%20on%20deck%20six%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20when%20I%20spotted%20a%20tattoo%20shop%20called%20Squid%20Ink.%20Virgin%20Voyages%20says%20it's%20the%20first%20cruise%20line%20to%20offer%20tattooing%20on%20board.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cruisegear.com%2Fvirgin-voyages-review-complete-guide%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECruise%20Gear%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20tattoo%20pricing%20starts%20at%20about%20%24150.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20getting%20tattooed%2C%20so%20seeing%20the%20shop%20excited%20me%2C%20but%20I%20resisted%20the%20urge%20to%20get%20one%20on%20this%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWith%20so%20many%20high-end%20restaurants%20on%20board%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20that%20none%20of%20the%20food%20cost%20extra.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20entrance%20to%20a%20restaurant%20called%20Gunbae%20with%20a%20neon%20sign%20on%20the%20left%20and%20a%20view%20of%20the%20dining%20room%20on%20the%20right%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e38d88bd98a600197aff86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20first%20cruise%20on%20board%20Royal%20Caribbean's%20Wonder%20of%20the%20Seas%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20food%20on%20the%20ship%20was%20included%20in%20the%20ticket%20price%2C%20but%20specialty%20restaurants%20incurred%20an%20additional%20price.%20Many%20cruise%20lines%20operate%20this%20way%2C%20so%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20learn%20that%20none%20of%20the%20food%20on%20my%20Virgin%20Voyages%20cruise%20cost%20extra.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20all-inclusive%20dining%20was%20especially%20shocking%2C%20given%20the%20upscale%20restaurants%20offering%20everything%20from%20fresh%20pasta%20and%20Mediterranean%20seafood%20to%20sushi%20and%20steak.%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20queen%20as%20I%20indulged%20in%20the%20opportunity%20to%20forget%20about%20finances%20while%20dining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20expected%20to%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20day%20drinkers%20on%20board%2C%20but%20the%20communal%20decks%20were%20calm%20during%20the%20day.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pool%20deck%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship%20with%20a%20large%20whirlpool%20on%20the%20right%20and%20a%20bar%20on%20the%20left%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fd3b62c6ad288d147e16de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20first%20cruise%2C%20I%20spotted%20many%20people%20drinking%20and%20partying%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20so%20I%20expected%20to%20see%20even%20more%20of%20that%20on%20an%20adults-only%20cruise.%20But%20the%20communal%20decks%20were%20surprisingly%20calm%20when%20the%20sun%20was%20up.%20It%20was%20easy%20to%20relax%20by%20the%20pools%20%E2%80%94%20one%20had%20music%20playing%2C%20while%20the%20other%20was%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20talked%20to%20a%20bartender%20about%20my%20differing%20experiences%2C%20and%20they%20said%20Mediterranean%20cruisers%20tended%20to%20be%20less%20interested%20in%20partying%20than%20Caribbean%20cruisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20last%20thing%20I%20expected%20from%20my%20adults-only%20cruise%20was%20to%20feel%20like%20a%20kid%20again.%20And%20that%20was%20the%20best%20surprise%20of%20all.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20the%20author%20smiling%20on%20a%20large%2C%20netted%20swing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fe89313fe8d39283631c87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20luxury%20ship%20without%20kids%2C%20I%20expected%20to%20enjoy%20my%20adults-only%20cruise%20more%20than%20my%20first%20cruise.%20But%20I%20didn't%20expect%20the%20Virgin%20Voyages%20cruise%20to%20make%20me%20feel%20like%20a%20child%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlaying%20for%20hours%20surrounded%20by%20rainbows%20and%20eating%20whatever%20I%20wanted%20without%20thinking%20about%20money%20allowed%20me%20to%20let%20loose%20in%20a%20way%20I%20hadn't%20in%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20definitely%20cruise%20with%20Virgin%20Voyages%20again%2C%20and%20maybe%20next%20time%2C%20I'll%20get%20some%20fresh%20ink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-voyages-adults-only-cruise-surprises%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780947954000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fd5169a466d2b74ab31de3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-voyages-adults-only-cruise-surprises%22%2C%