kers%20since%20Trump%20introduced%20it%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-h-1b-visa-fee-silicon-valley-tech-hiring-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%24100%2C000%20visa%20fee%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20H-1B%20applicants%20has%20hit%20a%20new%20legal%20roadblock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20judge%20at%20a%20US%20District%20Court%20in%20Massachusetts%20ruled%20Monday%20that%20the%20fee%20violates%20the%20Constitution's%20Administrative%20Procedure%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJudge%20Leo%20Sorokin%20found%20that%20the%20fee%20is%20%26quot%3Bunlawful%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.mad.293201%2Fgov.uscourts.mad.293201.106.0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eruling%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Sorokin%20said%20the%20fee%20constitutes%20a%20tax%20and%20requires%20congressional%20approval%20to%20implement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20implementation%20of%20the%20%24100%2C000%20fee%20for%20new%20petitions%20using%20an%20executive%20order%20last%20year%20%26quot%3Bexceeds%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20President's%20discretionary%20authority%26quot%3B%20under%20US%20immigration%20law%2C%20Sorokin%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fee%20has%20faced%20legal%20challenges%20since%20Trump%20signed%20the%20executive%20order%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20has%20argued%20that%20companies%20have%20used%20the%20visa%20to%20replace%20US%20workers.%20Employees%20at%20tech%20companies%20are%20among%20the%20most%20common%20applicants%20for%20the%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20battle%20over%20whether%20the%20fee%20is%20constitutional%20will%20likely%20continue%2C%20the%20order%20has%20already%20had%20an%20effect.%20The%20number%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-google-amazon-microsoft-h-1b-visa-applications-decline-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EH-1B%20visa%20applications%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20such%20as%20Google%20and%20Microsoft%20fell%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%20after%20Trump%20signed%20the%20executive%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fee%20was%20previously%20as%20much%20as%20%245%2C000%20per%20visa%20before%20Trump%20made%20the%20change%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-judge-blocks-trump-100-000-h-1b-visa-fee-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780941554000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2700255bcf40c28b6b03bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-judge-blocks-trump-100-000-h-1b-visa-fee-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Monday%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20said%20Trump's%20%24100%2C000%20H-1B%20visa%20fee%20was%20unconstitutional.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22First%20time%20in%2026%20years%2C%20India%20Inc%20out%20of%20MSCI%20EM%20top%2010%20as%20AI%20stocks%20surge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780941505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-05%2F14%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X628%2F1747213457-9792.JPG%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Findia-inc-exits-msci-em-top-10-as-ai-driven-stocks-dominate-benchmark-126060801039_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20giants%20dominate%2C%20evoke%20concentration%20risk%20concerns%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Findia-inc-exits-msci-em-top-10-as-ai-driven-stocks-dominate-benchmark-126060801039_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22