%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-judge-strikes-down-donald-trumps-100k-visa-fee-calls-it-unlawful%2Famp_articleshow%2F131593698.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-judge-strikes-down-donald-trumps-100k-visa-fee-calls-it-unlawful%2Famp_articleshow%2F131593698.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20finally%20gives%20Siri%20an%20AI%20glow-up%20after%20rare%20delay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tim%20Cook%20waves%20during%20Apple's%202025%20WWDC%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26f19d0421ca48aa59fcd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221694%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETim%20Cook%20opened%20Apple's%20WWDC%202026%20keynote%20%E2%80%94%20his%20last%20as%20CEO.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20detailed%20its%20long-delayed%20overhaul%20to%20Siri%20at%20WWDC%202026.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tech%20giant's%20AI%20assistant%20is%20set%20to%20finally%20get%20AI-powered%20capabilities%2C%20some%20of%20which%20were%20initially%20teased%20in%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20announced%20a%20deal%20with%20Google%20in%20January%20to%20have%20Gemini%20power%20Siri's%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESiri's%20full-fledged%20AI%20moment%20is%20finally%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Apple%20unveiled%20its%20long-awaited%2C%20much-delayed%20overhaul%20of%20Siri%20as%20it%20looks%20to%20catch%20up%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20we%20are%20introducing%20an%20entirely%20new%20version%20of%20Siri%2C%20Siri%20unlocked%20by%20Apple%20Intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mike%20Rockwell%2C%20VP%20of%20engineering%2C%20said%20during%20the%20company's%202026%20Worldwide%20Developers%20Conference.%20%26quot%3BWe%20call%20it%20Siri%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Siri%20AI%20will%20exist%20within%20Apple's%20software%20ecosystem%20but%20also%20as%20a%20standalone%20app.%20The%20underlying%20architecture%20of%20the%20new%20Siri%20is%20the%20result%20of%20Apple's%20partnership%20earlier%20this%20year%20with%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERockwell%20showed%20Siri%20using%20a%20variety%20of%20AI-powered%20capabilities%2C%20including%20the%20ability%20to%20find%20previously%20sent%20addresses%2C%20photos%20from%20particular%20locations%2C%20and%20more%2C%20%26quot%3Busing%20your%20personal%20context.%26quot%3B%20In%20one%20example%2C%20Rockwell%20showed%20how%20Siri%20could%20find%20specific%20photos%20he%20needed%20and%20share%20them%20with%20a%20group%20without%20ever%20opening%20the%20Photos%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiri%20will%20have%20a%20brand%20new%20voice%20experience%20%26quot%3Bthat%20enables%20Siri%20to%20sound%20incredible%20and%20a%20lot%20more%20expressive.%26quot%3B%20Rockwell%20said%20users%20can%20also%20customize%20how%20expressive%20they%20want%20Siri%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221934%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Rockwell%20shows%20the%20capabilities%20of%20the%20new%20Siri%20during%20WWDC%202026%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26ff0d5bcf40c28b6b03a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221090%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMike%20Rockwell%20shows%20the%20capabilities%20of%20the%20new%20Siri%20during%20WWDC%202026%3Cp%3EApple%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20voice%20improvements%2C%20Rockwell%20said%20Siri%20is%20also%20getting%20a%20dictation%20improvement%20%26quot%3Bwith%20a%20major%20boost%20in%20accuracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20encountering%20product%20development%20delays%2C%20Apple%20reached%20a%20deal%20in%20January%20with%20Google%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-google-gemini-to-power-siri-ai-capabilities-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGemini%20power%20Siri's%20artificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20capabilities.%20Craig%20Federighi%2C%20Apple's%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20software%20engineering%2C%20detailed%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20collaboration%26quot%3B%20with%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTogether%2C%20we%20created%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20Apple%20Intelligence%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20Federighi%20said%20in%20a%20video%20played%20during%20the%20WWDC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Apple%20announced%20a%20massive%20update%20to%20Siri%2C%20promising%20a%20more%20%26quot%3Bnatural%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%26quot%3B%20assistant%20powered%20by%20Apple%20Intelligence.%20But%20then%20it%20ran%20into%20issues.%20By%20March%202025%2C%20Apple%20made%20the%20exceedingly%20rare%20move%20to%20announce%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-siri-ai-delay-rare-move-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESiri%20revamp%20was%20delayed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20also%20pulled%20down%20a%20September%202024%20ad%20featuring%20%26quot%3BThe%20Last%20of%20Us%26quot%3B%20star%20Bella%20Ramsey%20that%20featured%20Ramsey%20using%20Siri's%20AI%20to%20pull%20information%20from%20the%20calendar%20app%20to%20remember%20someone's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Apple%20agreed%20to%20pay%20%24250%20million%20to%20settle%20a%20class-action%20lawsuit%20accusing%20the%20company%20of%20misleading%20customers%20about%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-ai-siri-advertising-claims-watchdog-delay-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20availability%20of%20AI-enhanced%20features%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20analysts%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-wwdc-aapl-stock-ai-iphone-siri-gemini-tech-stocks-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclosely%20watching%20Apple's%20AI%20announcements%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20also%20Cook's%20final%20WWDC%20as%20CEO%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20last%20big%20opportunities%20for%20the%20legendary%20executive%20to%20rewrite%20Apple's%20AI%20struggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-new-siri-ai-chatbot-app-wwdc-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780940657000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26f1a76f4f6ea1de4d340b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-new-siri-ai-chatbot-app-wwdc-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20repeated%20delays%2C%20Apple's%20Siri%20is%20finally%20poised%20for%20a%20big%20AI%20overhaul.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20left%20NYC%20for%20the%20Connecticut%20coast.%20After%20less%20than%202%20years%20away%2C%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20city%20for%20good.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20leaning%20near%20water%20by%20bridge%20in%20New%20York%20City%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26eef15bcf40c28b6b0353%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222940%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20lasted%20less%20than%20two%20years%20living%20in%20Connecticut%20before%20I%20decided%20to%20move%20back%20to%20New%20York%20City%2C%20where%20I%20plan%20to%20stay.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Galante%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20many%20years%20of%20living%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-city-to-small-coastal-village-better-than-suburb-2025-7%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20the%20Connecticut%20coast%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20a%20while%2C%20I%20felt%20I%20was%20thriving%20among%20beautiful%20views%2C%20fresh%20air%2C%20and%20lower%20living%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAlmost%20two%20years%20later%2C%20I%20missed%20New%20York%20City%2C%20warts%20and%20all%2C%20and%20moved%20back.%20I'm%20so%20glad%20I%20did.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20set%20foot%20in%20Brooklyn%20was%20to%20look%20at%20an%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20vividly%20remember%20the%20slow%20chug%20of%20the%20M%20Train%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-shares-accepted-luxury-brooklyn-home-price-photos-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWilliamsburg%20Bridge%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20watching%20the%20Lower%20East%20Side%20shrink%20behind%20me%2C%20and%20the%20contour%20of%20the%20Kings%20County%20skyline%20approaching%20across%20the%20East%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%2023.%20I%20felt%20like%20I'd%20arrived%20and%20my%20future%20was%20limitless.%20I%20moved%20to%20that%20apartment.%20Shoebox%20would%20have%20been%20a%20generous%20description%20for%20my%20%24900%20a%20month%20room%20with%20Craigslist%20roommates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%20seven%20years%2C%20I%20bounced%20between%20North%20Brooklyn%20dwellings%2C%20my%20rent%20rising%20faster%20than%20inflation.%20By%20May%202023%2C%20I%20was%20paying%20%241%2C900%20a%20month%20to%20live%20with%20two%20roommates%20in%20a%20basement%20that%20had%20a%20tendency%20to%20flood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20it%20was%20a%20third-life%20crisis%2C%20maybe%20it%20was%20the%20natural%20progression%20of%20the%20American%20millennial%2C%20but%20sometimes%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20just%20needed%20to%20touch%20grass.%20So%20I%20did%20what%20many%20people%20before%20me%20had%20done%3A%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-california-countryside-perfect-place-get-old-pros-cons-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandmother%20had%20died%20about%20six%20months%20prior%2C%20and%20her%20home%20on%20the%20Connecticut%2FRhode%20Island%20border%20was%20about%20to%20sit%20empty%20for%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20situation%2C%20my%20disdain%20for%20my%20job%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20the%20impending%20end%20of%20my%20lease%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusing-birth-charts-figure-out-where-to-live-how-astrocartography-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecosmic%20sign%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20was%20meant%20to%20go%20coastal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20applied%20to%20a%20few%20seasonal%20restaurant%20jobs%20online%20and%20quickly%20secured%20employment.%20I%20sold%20my%20bed%20frame%2C%20desk%2C%20and%20dresser%2C%20loaded%20my%20late%20grandmother's%20Jeep%20with%20what%20remained%2C%20and%20put%20New%20York%20in%20the%20rearview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20officially%20become%20one%20of%20those%20people%20who%20%3Cem%3Eused%20to%3C%2Fem%3E%20live%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228e0990a6-996e-435d-a5b7-14d18cae255c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20a%20while%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20thriving%20in%20the%20pink%20cloud%20of%20the%20Connecticut%20coast%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20under%20Williamsburg%20bridge%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26eea6b4fb977f35985610%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20be%20out%20of%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Galante%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEconomic%20benefits%20aside%2C%20I%20took%20to%20country%20life%20at%20first.%20Waking%20to%20the%20sounds%20of%20chirping%20birds%20instead%20of%20honking%20horns%20was%20refreshing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20commute%20was%20now%20filled%20with%20the%20smell%20of%20freshly%20cut%20grass%20instead%20of%20literal%20garbage%2C%20and%20I%20was%20beholden%20to%20tourist%20traffic%20and%20streetlights%20instead%20of%20the%20L-train%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20no%20longer%20needed%20to%20go%20to%20a%20public%20park%20to%20look%20at%20trees%2C%20and%20I%20could%20enjoy%20the%20weather%20from%20a%20golf%20course%20or%20waterfront.%20Of%20course%2C%20I%20could've%20played%20golf%20or%20seen%20the%20sea%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20but%20the%20courses%20would%20probably%20have%20been%20more%20crowded%20and%20the%20water%20less%20picturesque.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20restaurant%20wages%20were%20lower%20than%20what%20I'd%20made%20at%20my%20corporate%20job%20in%20New%20York%2C%20but%20I%20no%20longer%20spent%20nearly%20half%20my%20income%20on%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20spending%20less%20on%20food%2C%20too.%20I%20always%20enjoyed%20cooking%2C%20but%20the%20ease%20and%20temptation%20of%20world-class%20cuisine%20often%20meant%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-eat-in-new-york-city-restaurants-according-to-local%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeating%20out%20in%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20weren't%20as%20many%20restaurants%20on%20the%20coast%2C%20and%20I%20frequently%20found%20myself%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20cooking%20local%20seafood%20and%20fresh%20vegetables%20from%20farmstands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20even%20cooked%20fish%20I'd%20caught%2C%20which%20I%20suppose%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.health.ny.gov%2Fpress%2Freleases%2F2026%2F2026-04-01_advice_for_eating_fish.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20possible%20in%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20(but%20only%20recently%20deemed%20safe).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f59b3b3-d356-47c3-bf37-6965617c05c0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20reckoning%20with%20the%20limits%20of%20my%20lifestyle%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20back%20in%20New%20York%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20smiling%20with%20dessert%20in%20a%20restaurant%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26eea62ab5f9757adda255%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20missed%20late-night%20dinners%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Galante%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20culture%20shock%20was%20mostly%20positive%20for%20a%20while%2C%20there%20were%20signs%20that%20my%20new%20reality%20conflicted%20with%20my%20conditioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20night%2C%20I%20left%20work%20famished%20around%208%20p.m.%20I%20looked%20up%20restaurants%20in%20the%20area%20and%20noticed%20most%20of%20the%20kitchens%20had%20either%20closed%20or%20would%20do%20so%20by%20the%20time%20I%20could%20drive%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20moment%20of%20desperation%2C%20I%20pulled%20into%20a%20Burger%20King%2C%20only%20to%20find%20that%20closed%20too.%20In%20Brooklyn%2C%20people%20would%20just%20now%20be%20heading%20to%20dinner%20%E2%80%94%20if%20I%20hurried%2C%20I%20might%20be%20able%20to%20catch%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20realization%20that%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-new-york-city-moved-back-hometown-what-i-miss-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emissed%20city%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Not%20long%20after%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20growing%20impatient%20with%20the%20line%20at%20a%20coffee%20shop%2C%20lamenting%20the%20price%20of%20gas%2C%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20local%20bacon%2C%20egg%2C%20and%20cheese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20looking%20toward%20subway%20entrance%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26eea62e5a80cfe050473c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEventually%2C%20just%20visiting%20New%20York%20City%20wasn't%20enough%20for%20me.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Galante%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-in-new-york-city-different-than-visiting-lessons-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisited%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20few%20times%20over%20that%20year.%20Leaving%20got%20harder%20each%20time.%20People%20on%20the%20coast%20often%20asked%20how%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%26quot%3B%20city%20life%20was%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20I%20often%20felt%20safer%20on%20the%20subway%20platform%20at%20midnight%20than%20I%20did%20driving%20on%20Connecticut's%20pitch-black%20backroads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20my%20new%20life%20had%20become%20unsustainable%20when%20I%20took%20the%20Amtrak%20down%20to%20the%20city%20on%20a%20hot%20August%20weekend.%20I%20exited%20Penn%20Station%20to%20the%20stickiness%20of%20Midtown%20and%20was%20greeted%20with%20thick%20air%20and%20a%20cacophony%20of%20horns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20acknowledged%20the%20objective%20unpleasantness%2C%20and%20yet%20I%20felt%20at%20ease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20it%20was%20part%20nostalgia%2C%20but%20if%20I%20missed%20the%20disgusting%20chaos%20of%20arguably%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20places%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20then%20maybe%20this%20was%20where%20I%20was%20meant%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20that%2C%20I%20started%20applying%20to%20jobs%20back%20in%20New%20York%20and%20scrolling%20various%20apartment%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22286f8912-bb65-4b51-b79f-7b11a318a4c4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20time%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I've%20returned%20home%20for%20good%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20standing%20in%20New%20York%20City%20near%20a%20deli%20at%20night%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26eebd2e5a80cfe0504740%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20feel%20like%20I'm%20truly%20at%20home%20now%20that%20I'm%20back%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Galante%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20November%2C%20I%20had%20two%20restaurant%20jobs%20lined%20up%20and%20met%20someone%20on%20Reddit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-rented-spare-room-save-money-mistakes-pros-cons-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erenting%20a%20cheap%20room%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20few%20blocks%20from%20one%20of%20my%20old%20apartments.%20I%20was%20going%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20back%20in%20Brooklyn%20now%20for%20about%20as%20long%20as%20I%20was%20away%2C%20a%20little%20over%20a%20year.%20The%20first%20few%20months%2C%20I%20worked%20almost%20every%20day%20just%20to%20cover%20rent%2C%20and%20felt%20a%20rude%20awakening%20every%20time%20I%20looked%20at%20my%20credit-card%20bill%20or%20bank%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20down%20to%20one%20job%20now%2C%20and%20while%20the%20financial%20pains%20are%20still%20real%2C%20at%20least%20I%20know%20where%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-chains-best-value-10-dollars-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eget%20a%20cheap%20meal%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20midnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20get%20a%20yearning%20for%20grass%20and%20fresh%20air.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20each%20month%2C%20I%20certainly%20yearn%20for%20cheaper%20living%20quarters%2C%20but%20not%20when%20I%20take%20the%20M%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20now%2C%20at%2032%20years%20old%20with%20a%20jaded%20lived%20reality%20and%20mounting%20bills%2C%20when%20I%20chug%20over%20the%20Williamsburg%20Bridge%2C%20I%20feel%2023.%20I%20see%20the%20city%20lights%20on%20every%20side%20of%20me%2C%20and%20I'm%20filled%20with%20this%20childlike%20wonder%20and%20optimism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20like%20I'm%20home%2C%20where%20anything%20is%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-new-york-city-moved-to-connecticut-cons-came-back-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780940546000%2C%22visual%22