3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-filing-going-public-investors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES-1%20filing%3C%2Fa%3E%20raises%20some%20concerns.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20what%20is%20probably%20most%20important%20in%20the%20prospectus%20is%20how%20capital-intensive%20SpaceX%20has%20become%2C%26quot%3B%20Eisman%20noted.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20go%20back%20to%20fiscal%20year%202023%20and%20you%20compare%20revenue%20to%20capex%2C%20capex%20was%20only%2042%25%20of%20revenue%2C%20and%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20first%20quarter%2C%20it%20was%20215%25%20of%20revenue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEisman%20attributed%20the%20capex%20surge%20to%20the%20significant%20AI%20buildout%20in%20which%20SpaceX%20has%20attempted%20to%20pivot%20toward%20branding%20itself%20as%20an%20AI%20services%20and%20infrastructure%20company%20company%20as%20opposed%20to%20a%20more%20pure-play%20space%20tech%20firm.%20In%20his%20view%2C%20the%20AI%20endeavors%20are%20making%20the%20company%20too%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-elon-musk-starlink-s1-ai-stocks-markets-investing-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecapital%20intensive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20contributing%20to%20his%20pessimistic%20view.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20he%20doesn't%20view%20Grok%20as%20a%20leading%20AI%20model%2C%20and%20despite%20SpaceX's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-anthropic-paying-ai-compute-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompute%20partnership%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20leading%20AI%20startup%20Anthropic%2C%20he%20still%20sees%20the%20company's%20business%20as%20overly%20capital%20intensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEisman%20added%20that%20he%20thinks%20the%20most%20important%20news%20story%20of%20the%20past%20week%20is%20Google's%20%2480%20billion%20capital%20raise%2C%20because%20it%20highlights%20just%20how%20capital%20intensive%20the%20entire%20tech%20sector%20has%20become%2C%20with%20the%20whole%20business%20model%20shifting%20from%20asset-light%20to%20asset-heavy%20as%20the%20data%20center%20buildout%20continues%20at%20breakneck%20pace.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20incredible%20sums%20of%20money%20that%20are%20being%20spent%2C%20what's%20being%20produced%20in%20terms%20of%20LLMs%20and%20agentic%20AI%2C%20which%20is%20great%2C%20is%20not%20really%20differentiable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20commoditized.%20People%20are%20switching%20constantly%20from%20one%20to%20the%20other.%20There%20are%20no%20moats%2C%20so%20for%20all%20the%20money%20that's%20being%20spent%2C%20what's%20being%20created%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20me%2C%20is%20a%20commodity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEisman%20also%20addressed%20the%20topic%20of%20betting%20against%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20responding%20to%20the%20argument%20that%20as%20a%20CEO%2C%20he%20has%20constantly%20found%20new%20ways%20to%20survive%20and%20innovate%2C%20even%20when%20faced%20with%20multiple%20headwinds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20didn't%20deny%20Musk's%20record%20of%20success%2C%20Eisman%20reiterated%20his%20concerns%20about%20the%20capital%20intensive%20nature%20of%20SpaceX's%20business%2C%20highlighting%20what%20he%20sees%20as%20an%20over%20reliance%20on%20costly%20AI%20in%20a%20market%20where%20uncertainty%20is%20still%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20company%20is%20being%20bet%20on%20AI%20in%20terms%20of%20its%20future%2C%20not%20on%20space%20and%20not%20on%20Starlink%2C%26quot%3B%20Eisman%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-steve-eisman-big-short-elon-musk-ai-spcx-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780935422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a26b635b4fb977f359854ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-steve-eisman-big-short-elon-musk-a