%20cafes%20in%20California.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20tried%20setting%20zones%20of%20the%20house%20and%20days%20of%20the%20week%20to%20avoid%20business%20talk.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUltimately%2C%20they%20realized%20they%20needed%20a%20more%20integrated%20communication%20technique.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Mojo%20and%20Zainab%20Joyo%2C%20owners%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elaichico.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EElaichi%20Co%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20missing%20a%20very%20specific%20piece%20of%20my%20childhood%3A%20sitting%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-place-to-get-an-iced-chai-photos-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echai%20caf%C3%A9s%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Pakistan%20with%20my%20cousins.%20We'd%20be%20together%2C%20late%20at%20night%2C%20sharing%20stories%20and%20enjoying%20quality%20time%20together%20%E2%80%94%20and%20chai%20was%20at%20the%20center%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20recreate%20that%20feeling%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20social%20isolation%20of%20the%20pandemic.%20My%20wife%20Zainab%20and%20I%20talked%20about%20how%20to%20do%20that%2C%20and%20finally%2C%20in%202024%2C%20we%20had%20the%20courage%20to%20open%20Elaichi%20Co.%2C%20a%20chai%20caf%C3%A9%20in%20Berkeley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20we%20were%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwrote-book-working-full-time-productivity-habits-helped-sacrificing-sleep-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20full-time%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20running%20the%20company.%20Zainab%2C%20especially%2C%20felt%20a%20lot%20of%20social%20pressure%20to%20hold%20onto%20a%20stable%20job.%20But%20when%20she%20was%20laid%20off%20in%20November%202024%2C%20we%20decided%20she%20would%20work%20at%20Elaichi%20full-time%2C%20while%20I%20continued%20with%20my%20day%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242c0706d-5b51-4cc2-a135-f1dc5668e6c6%5C%22%3EI%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20living%20with%20my%20business%20partner%2C%20not%20my%20wife%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EZainab%20was%20wearing%20many%20hats%3A%20marketing%2C%20events%2C%20HR%2C%20inventory%2C%20and%20more.%20When%20I%20got%20home%2C%20she'd%20fill%20me%20in%20on%20everything%20I%20needed%20to%20know%20about.%20It%20wasn't%20long%20before%20we%20realized%20that%20about%2095%25%20of%20our%20conversations%20were%20about%20the%20business.%20That%20wasn't%20what%20we%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20the%20right%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tools-save-15-hours-week-big-tech-founder-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20helped%20some.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20get%20quick%20insight%20into%20our%20finances%20without%20getting%20into%20the%20weeds%20when%20we%20started%20using%20the%20fintech%20company%2C%C2%A0Mercury.%20Yet%20tools%20alone%20weren't%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20only%20been%20married%20a%20few%20years%2C%20but%20Zainab%20wasn't%20getting%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Femotional-support-animal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemotional%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20needed%20from%20her%20husband%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20living%20with%20my%20business%20partner%2C%20not%20my%20wife.%20Business%20kept%20getting%20in%20the%20way%20of%20our%20relationship%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c088029e-399b-4f26-bbac-0889acf2b224%5C%22%3EWe%20made%20the%20bedroom%20and%20dining%20room%20business%20free%20zones%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20of%20us%20found%20it%20frustrating%20to%20lie%20in%20bed%20at%20night%2C%20only%20to%20have%20the%20other%20person%20bring%20up%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquestions-to-ask-in-a-job-interview-2016-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebusiness%20question%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20decided%20to%20designate%20certain%20areas%20of%20the%20house%20for%20personal%20talk%20only%2C%20not%20for%20business.%20The%20bedroom%20and%20dining%20room%20were%20spaces%20for%20our%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sounded%20great%20in%20theory%2C%20but%20it%20was%20inevitable%20that%20someone%20would%20bring%20business%20up%20when%20it%20popped%20into%20their%20head.%20If%20Zainab%20asked%20me%20a%20business%20question%20and%20I%20reminded%20her%20about%20our%20rule%20%E2%80%94%20no%20business%20talk%20in%20bed%20%E2%80%94%20she'd%20just%20be%20even%20more%20frustrated.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20abandoned%20this%20approach%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f768d3b9-28dc-4d60-bede-39dcc8e67dc6%5C%22%3EDesignating%20family%20days%20didn't%20work%20well%20either%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20we%20tried%20blocking%20off%20certain%20days%20of%20the%20week%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraised-son-to-care-about-family-time-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Saturday%20night%20was%20for%20us%20as%20a%20couple%2C%20and%20Sundays%20were%20for%20extended%20family.%20This%20worked%20much%20better%2C%20and%20we%20were%20able%20to%20stick%20with%20it%20for%20about%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20owners%2C%20however%2C%20we%20were%20always%20on%20call.%20If%20an%20employee%20called%20out%20or%20there%20was%20a%20big%20event%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20be%20there.%20It%20was%20hard%20to%20maintain%20the%20rhythm%20of%20family%20days%20when%20we%20were%20constantly%20being%20thrown%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276f9b122-50cf-4e77-868c-db859fbf1b0e%5C%22%3EWe%20stopped%20fighting%20against%20business%20talk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20came%20to%20a%20head%20about%20a%20year%20ago.%20We%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-never-felt-unsafe-in-puerto-vallarta-until-this-week-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuerto%20Vallarta%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Zainab's%2030th%20birthday.%20It%20should%20have%20been%20a%20great%20trip%20with%20just%20the%20two%20of%20us%2C%20but%20we%20felt%20disconnected%20throughout.%20We%20didn't%20like%20that%20we%20were%20still%20unhappy%20with%20how%20our%20relationship%20was%20going%2C%20despite%20trying%20different%20solutions.%20Neither%20our%20marriage%20nor%20our%20business%20was%20going%20to%20succeed%20unless%20something%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20we%20got%20back%2C%20we%20shifted%20from%20talking%20about%20our%20rules%20to%20thinking%20about%20why%20we%20were%20using%20them.%20We%20realized%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20fit%20into%20other%20people's%20ideas%20of%20what%20makes%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-youre-in-a-strong-relationship-2017-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20really%20enjoy%20running%20our%20business%20together%2C%20and%20we%20realized%20that%20if%20we%20were%20having%20fun%20talking%20about%20Elaichi%2C%20that%20was%20OK.%20We%20don't%20have%20to%20force%20ourselves%20to%20have%20a%20business-free%20night%20out%20together%20if%20we're%20actually%20really%20excited%20about%20working%20on%20a%20new%20business%20project%20together.%20Fighting%20against%20that%20had%20actually%20been%20making%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftime-to-rethink-what-work-life-balance-really-means-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework-life%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd6bfa8b-967a-40ea-8a36-b67624ce3646%5C%22%3EI'm%20doing%20business%20with%20my%20life%20partner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20we've%20had%20more%20fluid%20boundaries%20between%20our%20marriage%20and%20our%20business%20partnership.%20We%20focus%20on%20what%20we%20want%20to%20do%20together%2C%20rather%20than%20on%20arbitrary%20boundaries%20that%20we%20thought%20we%20needed.%20If%20we%20want%20to%20have%20a%20date%20night%2C%20we%20do%3B%20but%20we%20also%20sometimes%20talk%20about%20business%20at%20the%20dinner%20table%2C%20because%20it's%20something%20we're%20both%20passionate%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20defused%20a%20lot%20of%20tension%2C%20and%20we're%20able%20to%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%20quickly%20and%20more%20honestly.%20We%20have%20a%20level%20of%20trust%20and%20understanding%20that%20we%20don't%20have%20with%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20I%20no%20longer%20feel%20like%20I'm%20living%20with%20my%20business%20partner%3B%20I%20feel%20I'm%20doing%20business%20with%20my%20life%20partner.%20That's%20a%20much%20better%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-opening-business-relationship-strain-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780933981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a15cd2e3fd8f13891958054%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-opening-business-relationship-strain-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mojo%20and%20Zainab%20Joyo%20say%20running%20a%20chai%20caf%C3%A9%20together%20blurred%20the%20lines%20between%20marriage%20and%20business%20%E2%80%94%20until%20they%20changed%20their%20approach.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Valuations%2C%20growth%20prospects%20to%20limit%20downside%20risks%20for%20SBI%20Card%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780933763000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-02%2F06%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X6