%3Cli%3EM.%20Laxmikanth%20for%20Polity.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOnline%20research%20and%20YouTube%20lectures%20for%20Jharkhand-specific%20topics%2C%20since%20most%20standard%20books%20weren%E2%80%99t%20available%20in%20English.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrevious%20Year%20Questions%20(PYQs)%20as%20her%20strongest%20tool.%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20JPSC%20questions%20repeat%20in%20some%20form.%20So%2C%20PYQs%20were%20a%20blessing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mantra%20was%20simple%3A%20read%20less%2C%20revise%20more.%20She%20made%20detailed%20notes%2C%20revised%20them%20multiple%20times%2C%20and%20stuck%20to%20one%20source%20instead%20of%20chasing%20dozens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20believe%20that%20coaching%20is%20necessary%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20every%20aspirant%2C%20it%20is%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rupam%20stresses.%20%E2%80%9CConsistency%2C%20patience%2C%20and%20determination%20are%20far%20more%20important%20than%20expensive%20coaching%20classes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20result%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20July%20at%203%3A30%20am%2C%20Rupam%20received%20a%20call%20from%20a%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20who%20had%20taken%20her%20mock%20interview.%20The%20words%20on%20the%20other%20end%20left%20her%20stunned%3A%20%E2%80%9CRupam%2C%20you%20have%20cleared%20JPSC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%20half-asleep%2C%20she%20was%20first%20shocked%2C%20then%20overwhelmed.%20Her%20sister%2C%20who%20had%20stood%20by%20her%20through%20every%20storm%2C%20burst%20into%20tears%20of%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20day%2C%20Rupali%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20overwhelming%20%E2%80%94%20tears%2C%20laughter%2C%20disbelief%20all%20at%20once.%20For%20me%2C%20her%20success%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20clearing%20an%20exam%3B%20it%20was%20proof%20that%20all%20the%20sacrifices%2C%20all%20the%20hardships%2C%20and%20the%20lessons%20our%20mother%20had%20instilled%20in%20us%20had%20carried%20us%20through.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%20not%20everyone%20reacted%20the%20same.%20Some%20people%20celebrated%2C%20while%20others%20compared%2C%20saying%20she%20was%20lucky%2C%20their%20child%20wasn%E2%80%99t.%20But%20I%20believe%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20balance%20of%20fate%20and%20hard%20work.%20Roopam%20worked%20tirelessly%2C%20and%20destiny%20met%20her%20halfway%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rupali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-3-1757075513.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%2022%2C%20Rupam%20cleared%20JPSC%20in%20her%20first%20attempt%2C%20without%20coaching%20and%20against%20all%20odds.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-3-1757075513.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-3-1757075513-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-3-1757075513-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-3-1757075513-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-3-1757075513-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496980%5C%22%20hei