p-element-caption%5C%22%3EBrijith%20offers%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20value-added%20products%20such%20as%20cashew%20sprouts%2C%20soup%20premix%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReality%20of%20the%20largest%20cashew%20producers%20of%20Kerala%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Status%20of%20Cashew%20Research%20and%20Development%20in%20India%3A%20A%20State%20Perspective%20published%20by%20the%20ICAR-%20Directorate%20of%20Cashew%20Research%2C%20Karnataka%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20coastal%20state%20of%20Kerala%20accounts%20for%2015%20percent%20of%20cashew%20production%20in%20India.%20Of%20this%2C%20Kannur%20district%20accounts%20for%20nearly%2063%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20cashew%20cultivation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECashew%20production%20is%20relatively%20high%20in%20Kannur%20because%20the%20region%20experiences%20a%20prolonged%20dry%20spell%20during%20the%20reproductive%20phase%20of%20the%20crop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrijith%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20the%20same%20district%20and%20grows%20cashew%20on%2013%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20shares%20that%20cashew%20productivity%20has%20been%20affected%20amid%20unseasonal%20rain%20and%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20experience%20unseasonal%20rains%20in%20March-May.%20This%20affects%20the%20pollination%20process%20and%20the%20harvesting%20period.%20We%20are%20small%20farmers%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20good%20storage%20facilities.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20have%20to%20keep%20our%20harvest%20out%20in%20the%20open.%20Most%20of%20this%20produce%20gets%20wet%20in%20this%20period%20then.%20No%20cashew%20factory%20is%20ready%20to%20purchase%20this%20damaged%20product%20as%20its%20quality%20becomes%20poor%2C%20colour%20gets%20faded%2C%20and%20also%20has%20a%20poor%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%2047-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C